ld%20killer%20in%20the%20UK's%20modern%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20Letby%20killed%20infants%20by%20injecting%20air%20into%20their%20bloodstreams%20or%20feeding%20tubes%2C%20overfeeding%20them%20with%20milk%2C%20or%20poisoning%20them%20with%20insulin%2C%20she%20was%20also%20sending%20disturbing%20messages%20to%20colleagues%20that%20eventually%20served%20as%20crucial%20evidence%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-nurse-33-found-guilty-of-killing-seven-babies-4309643%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%26quot%3BI%20Am%20Evil...%26quot%3B%3A%20British%20Nurse%20Guilty%20Of%20Killing%207%20Newborns%20In%20A%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20text%20messages%20revealed%20that%20she%20had%20contacted%20her%20colleagues%20following%20the%20infants'%20deaths%20and%2C%20in%20response%2C%20received%20sympathy%20from%20unaware%20staff%20members.%20The%20messages%20also%20indicated%20that%20she%20volunteered%20to%20take%20on%20additional%20shifts%20in%20the%20neonatal%20intensive%20therapy%20unit%20(ITU)%20at%20the%20Countess%20of%20Chester%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-66120198%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ethe%20BBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20unsettling%20text%20messages%20illustrate%20her%20reactions%20as%20concerns%20escalated%20regarding%20the%20sudden%20increase%20in%20infant%20fatalities%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20excerpts%20of%20text%20messages%20that%20Lucy%20Letby%20sent%20to%20her%20colleagues%20over%20the%20course%20of%20her%2012-month%20period%20of%20heinous%20actions%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%209%2C%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%208th%2C%20Letby%20claimed%20her%20first%20victim%2C%20identified%20as%20Baby%20A.%20Following%20that%20incident%2C%20she%20messaged%20colleagues%2C%20expressing%20her%20reluctance%20to%20go%20back%20and%20face%20the%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20had%20Baby%20B%2C%20whom%20she%20attacked%20sometime%20before%20June%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%3Cem%3EDad%20was%20on%20the%20floor%20crying%2C%20saying%20please%20don't%20take%20our%20baby%20away%20when%20I%20took%20him%20to%20the%20mortuary%3B%20it's%20just%20heartbreaking.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20the%20hardest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20had%20to%20do.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20June%2011%2C%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20merely%20three%20days%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Baby%20A%2C%20Letby%20contacted%20a%20manager%20and%20requested%20to%20take%20on%20extra%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%3Cem%3EFrom%20a%20confidence%20point%20of%20view%2C%20I%20need%20to%20take%20an%20ITU%20baby%20soon%20X.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2013%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20messaged%20a%20colleague%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20just%20keep%20thinking%20about%20Mon%20(death%20of%20Child%20A).%20Feel%20like%20I%20need%20to%20be%20in%20(room)%201%20to%20overcome%20it...%20to%20get%20the%20image%20out%20of%20my%20head.%20It%20probably%20sounds%20odd%2C%20but%20it's%20how%20I%20feel.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20added%3A%20%3Cem%3EOnly%20those%20who%20saw%20him%20know%20what%20image%20I%20have%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20six%20minutes%20after%20their%20conversation%20ended%2C%20baby%20C%2C%20a%20baby%20boy%2C%20became%20severely%20unwell%20and%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2014%2C%202015%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20engaged%20in%20another%20conversation%20with%20the%20same%20colleague%20she%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20previous%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20just%20keep%20seeing%20them%20both.%20No%20one%20should%20have%20to%20see%20%26amp%3B%20do%20the%20things%20we%20do.%20It's%20heart-breaking.%20But%20it's%20not%20about%20me.%20We%20learn%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20It's%20not%20about%20me%20or%20anyone%20else%2C%20it's%20those%20poor%20parents%20who%20have%20to%20walk%20away%20without%20their%20baby.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2022%202015%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20the%20day%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Baby%20D%2C%20Letby%20once%20again%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%3Cem%3EOn%20a%20day%20to%20day%20basis%20it's%20an%20incredible%20job%20with%20so%20many%20positives.%20But%20sometimes%20I%20think%2C%20how%20do%20such%20sick%20babies%20get%20through%20%26amp%3B%20others%20just%20die%20so%20suddenly%20and%20unexpectedly%3F%20Guess%20it's%20how%20it's%20meant%20to%20be...%20I%20think%20there%20is%20an%20element%20of%20fate%20involved.%20There%20is%20a%20reason%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Cstrong%3EJune%2030%2C%202015%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20a%20nurse%20raised%20questions%20over%20the%20sudden%20changes%20in%20the%20health%20of%20babies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENurse%3A%20%3Cem%3EThere's%20something%20odd%20about%20that%20night%20and%20the%20other%20three%20that%20went%20so%20suddenly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%3A%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Well%2C%20Baby%20C%20was%20tiny%20and%20obviously%20compromised%20in%20utero.%20Baby%20D%20is%20septic.%20It's%20Baby%20A%20that%20I%20can't%20get%20my%20head%20around.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAugust%204%2C%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Baby%20E%20dies%2C%20while%20his%20twin%20brother%2C%20Baby%20F%2C%20remains%20in%20the%20ward.%20A%20colleague%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20Letby%2C%20inquiring%20whether%20she%20has%20been%20responsible%20for%20looking%20after%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%3A%3Cem%3E%20'News%20travels%20fast.%20Who%20told%20you%3F'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E'Yeah%20I%20had%20them%20both.%20Was%20horrible.'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENurse%3A%3Cem%3E%20'I%20just%20really%20feel%20for%20his%20parents%20but%20for%20you%20too.%20You've%20had%20some%20really%20tough%20times%20recently.'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%3A%20%3Cem%3E'Not%20a%20lot%20I%20can%20do%20really.%20He%20had%20massive%20haemorrhage%20could%20have%20happened%20to%20any%20baby%20x.'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAugust%205%2C%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20Baby%20E's%20death%2C%20Baby%20F%20experienced%20a%20critical%20decline%20in%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%3A%3Cem%3E%20I%20said%20goodbye%20to%20Baby%20F's%20parents%2C%20as%20Baby%20F%20might%20go%20tomorrow.%20They%20both%20cried%20and%20hugged%20me%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20never%20be%20able%20to%20thank%20me%20for%20the%20love%20and%20care%20I%20gave%20to%20Baby%20F%20and%20for%20the%20precious%20memories%20I've%20given%20them.%20It's%20heartbreaking%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENurse%3A%20%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20heartbreaking%2C%20but%20you've%20done%20your%20job%20to%20the%20highest%20standard%20with%20compassion%20and%20professionalism.%20%5B...%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20just%20feel%20sad%20that%20they%20are%20thanking%20me%20when%20they%20have%20lost%20him%20and%20for%20something%20that%20any%20of%20us%20would%20have%20done.%20But%20it's%20really%20nice%20to%20know%20that%20I%20got%20it%20right%20for%20them.%20That's%20all%20I%20want.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692419700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcae0k2rg_lucy-letby_625x300_19_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frevealed-disturbing-text-messages-sent-by-killer-nurse-lucy-letby-during-murder-spree-4310597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20text%20messages%20sent%20by%20the%20killer%20nurse%2C%20Lucy%20Letby%2C%20emerged%20as%20crucial%20evidence%20in%20the%20case%20against%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen