0they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20infiltration%20is%20taking%20place%20from%20these%20areas.%20If%20attempts%20are%20being%20thwarted%20by%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20another%20group%20going%20undetected%20are%20relatively%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20on%20the%20ground%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20Pakistan's%20strategy%20is%20clear%20--%20even%20if%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20of%20infiltrators%20get%20shot%20down%20in%20encounters%2C%20they%20will%20keep%20pushing%20more%20terrorists.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20all-weather%20route%2C%20so%20that%20also%20works%20in%20their%20advantage%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20easily%20cross%20over%20to%20the%20valley%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rising%20casualties%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20in%20the%20area%20have%20forced%20them%20to%20a%20reshuffle%20in%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%2C%20a%20total%20of%2026%20security%20personnel%2C%20including%20three%20officers%2C%20five%20paratroopers%2C%20and%20seven%20civilians%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20these%20areas%20since%20October%2021%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgencies%20have%20also%20warned%20security%20forces%20operating%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20a%20rise%20in%20infiltration%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCordon%20and%20search%20operations%20are%20now%20an%20everyday%20affair.%20We%20keep%20hearing%20about%20encounters%20and%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhiraj%20Sharma%2C%20Sarpanch%20of%20the%20Dangri%20village%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20region%20was%20relatively%20calmer%20since%20the%20mid-2000s%2C%20after%20being%20a%20hotbed%20of%20insurgency%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%20But%20lately%2C%20the%20twin%20district%20has%20seen%20alarming%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Galwan%2C%20forces%20were%20thinned%20down%20in%20this%20area%2C%20but%20now%20arithmetic%20is%20being%20worked%20out%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20level%20officer%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20terrorists%20are%20now%20targeting%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20belt%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20%26quot%3Bafter%20suffering%20setbacks%20in%20Kashmir%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20more%20aggressive%20CASO%20(cordon%20and%20search%20operations)%20intelligence%20based%20operations%20are%20being%20executed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20also%20hinted%20that%20fresh%20strategy%20is%20being%20adopted%20by%20security%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20the%20twin%20border%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20recent%20Human%20Rights%20Report%20released%20by%20the%20Forum%20of%20Human%20Rights%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20also%20highlighted%20this%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20decades%20of%20peace%2C%20the%20bordering%20areas%20of%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20in%20Jammu%20division%20are%20re-emerging%20as%20a%20locus%20for%20militancy%20with%20cross-border%20support%20from%20Pakistan-held%20territories%20of%20the%20former%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20compiled%20by%20a%20group%20of%2018%20which%20includes%20former%20Home%20Secretary%20GK%20Pillai%2C%20former%20foreign%20secretary%20Nirupama%20Rao%2C%20and%20Radha%20Kumar%2C%20former%20interlocutor%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20highlights%20that%20the%202022%20delimitation%20of%20fresh%20legislative%20constituencies%2C%20adding%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20of%20Jammu%20region%20to%20Kashmir's%20Anantnag%2C%20may%20have%20added%20to%20the%20alienation%20that%20these%20Muslim-majority%20areas%20face%20with%20the%20sharpening%20of%20communal%20divides%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncreasing%20weaponisation%20through%20Jammu's%20village%20defence%20guards%2C%20a%20problematic%20policy%20that%20the%20Forum%20highlighted%20in%20its%202022%20report%2C%20has%20added%20further%20insecurity%20in%20the%20region.%20As%20has%20the%202023%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20which%20has%20pitted%20Paharis%20against%20Gujjars%20and%20other%20listed%20scheduled%20tribes%20of%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692419100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F1r2rd56o_rajouri-encounter-pti_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-border-infiltration-along-rajouri-and-poonch-security-deployment-reshuffled-as-j-ks-twin-districts-back-on-terror-radar-4310605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20cross-border%20infiltration%20is%20at%20its%20lowest%20this%20year%2C%20so%20far%2C%20security%20agencies%20have%20raised%20an%20alarm%20about%20an%20increase%20in%20activity%20at%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20along%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20border%20districts%20of%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-border-infiltration-along-rajouri-and-poonch-security-deployment-reshuffled-as-j-ks-twin-districts-back-on-terror-radar-4310605%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-border-infiltration-along-rajouri-and-poonch-security-deployment-reshuffled-as-j-ks-twin-districts-back-on-terror-radar-4310605%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-border-infiltration-along-rajouri-and-poonch-security-deployment-reshuffled-as-j-ks-twin-districts-back-on-terror-radar-4310605%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWorld%20's%20Largest...%26quot%3B%3A%20WHO%20Chief%20Praises%20India's%20Ayushman%20Health%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDr%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%2C%20Director-General%20of%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20on%20Friday%20praised%20India%20for%20advancing%20health%20coverage%20and%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Tedros%20made%20the%20remarks%20while%20addressing%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20ongoing%20G20%20Health%20Ministers'%20Meeting%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20begining%20of%20his%20address%2C%20Dr%20Tedros%20thanked%20India%20for%20its%20gracious%20hospitality%20and%20visionary%20leadership%20in%20hosting%20the%20G20%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20commend%20India%20for%20their%20steps%20in%20advancing%20Universal%20Health%20Coverage%20and%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20which%20is%20the%20world%20's%20largest%20health%20assurance%20initiative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WHO%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recalled%20his%20visit%20to%20a%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centre%20and%20lauded%20the%20services%20being%20provided%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20visited%20a%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centre%20here%20in%20Gandhinagar%20and%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20primary%20healthcare%20services%20being%20provided%20to%201000%20households%20by%20the%20HWC%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20hailed%20the%20telemedicine%20facilities%20provided%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20thanked%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%20for%20the%20Global%20Digital%20Health%20Initiative%20to%20be%20launched%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20commend%20the%20telemedicine%20services%20being%20provided%20here%2C%20which%20provide%20prescriptions%20and%20treatment%20locally.%20It%20is%20an%20excellent%20example%20of%20transforming%20healthcare.%20I%20also%20thank%20India%20G20%20Presidency%20for%20taking%20leadership%20in%20the%20Global%20Digital%20Health%20Initiative%20which%20will%20be%20launched%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Tedros%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20more%20than%2070%20delegates%20from%20different%20countries%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20G20%20Health%20Ministers'%20meeting%20and%20side%20event%20in%20Gandhinagar%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-day%20G20%20Health%20Ministers'%20meeting%20under%20G20%20India%20Presidency%20will%20culminate%20on%20August%2019.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2070%20delegates%20from%20different%20countries%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20G20%20Health%20Ministers'%20meeting%20and%20side%20events.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20showing%20India's%20Health%20model%20to%20the%20people%20and%20they%20are%20appreciating%20it.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20seen%20the%20health%20sector%20with%20a%20holistic%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mandaviya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20Health%20Ministers'%20meeting%20under%20G20%20India%20Presidency%20is%20being%20held%20during%20from%20August%2017%20to%2019%20at%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20assumed%20the%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20on%20December%201%2C%202022%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20part%20of%20the%20G20%20Troika%20comprising%20Indonesia%2C%20India%20and%20Brazil.%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%20marked%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20troika%20is%20consisting%20of%20three%20developing%20and%20emerging%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20of%20the%20G20%20Health%20Minister's%20Meeting%20will%20be%20on%20the%20three%20key%20priorities%20of%20the%20G20%20Health%20Track%2C%20including%20health%20emergencies%20prevention%2C%20preparedness%20and%20response%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20anti-microbial%20resistance%20and%20One%20Health%20framework%3B%20Strengthening%20cooperation%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20sector%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20access%20and%20availability%20to%20safe%2C%20effective%2C%20quality%20and%20affordable%20medical%20countermeasures%20(Vaccines%2C%20Therape