%2F102849290.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDirected%20by%20Amit%20Rai%2C%20'OMG%202'%20is%20a%20spiritual%20sequel%20to%202021%20release%20'OMG%20-%20Oh%20My%20God'.%20This%20film%20stars%20Akshay%20Kumar%2C%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20and%20Yami%20Gautam%20in%20lead%20roles.%20'OMG%202'%20has%20managed%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20despite%20facing%20competition%20from%20'Gadar%202'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Nervous%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Bumrah's%201st%20Reaction%20On%20Being%20MoM%20On%20Injury%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%20took%20only%20two%20balls%20to%20get%20his%20first%20international%20wicket%20in%20about%2011%20months%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20His%20return%20was%20an%20eagerly%20anticipated%20one%20for%20the%20side%20ahead%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%202023.%20And%20against%20Ireland%20Bumrah%20made%20it%20extra-special%20by%20returning%20with%20figures%20of%202%2F24%20to%20grab%20the%20player-of-the-match%20award%20on%20his%20international%20return%2C%20on%20Friday%20said%20he%20was%20not%20nervous%20and%20never%20felt%20he%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20out%20a%20lot%26quot%3B.%20Bumrah%20took%20the%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20over%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20last%20featured%20for%20India%20exactly%20327%20days%20back%20in%20a%20bilateral%20T20I%20series%20at%20home%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20back%20injury%20would%20rule%20him%20out%20from%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202022%20in%20Australia%2C%20with%20the%20pacer%20undergoing%20surgery%20and%20beginning%20a%20prolonged%20rehabilitation%20process%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20really%20nervous%20but%20very%20happy%20to%20be%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20returned%20with%202%20for%2024%2C%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20captaining%20you%20are%20thinking%20more%20about%20the%20whole%20team%20and%20not%20just%20your%20own%20performance.%26quot%3B%20Captaining%20a%20second-string%20side%20against%20Ireland%20in%20Malahide%20here%20on%20his%20comeback%2C%20Bumrah%20led%20India%20to%20a%20two-run%20win%20over%20Ireland%20by%20DLS%20Method%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20three-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20very%20good.%20So%20many%20sessions%20I%20did%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%20didn't%20feel%20I%20missed%20out%20a%20lot%20or%20was%20doing%20something%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCredit%20to%20the%20staff%20there%2C%20they%20kept%20me%20in%20good%20spirits.%20You%20are%20not%20thinking%20about%20yourself%2C%20you%20are%20thinking%20about%20others%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20IPL%20also%20helps.%20It%20is%20always%20good%2C%20wherever%20we%20go%2C%20they%20support%20us%2C%20that%20helps%20us%20to%20keep%20the%20spirit%20high.%26quot%3B%20Opting%20to%20field%2C%20Bumrah%20had%20a%20perfect%20start%2C%20grabbing%20two%20wickets%20giving%20away%20just%20two%20runs%20in%20his%20first%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20swing%20upfront%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20use%20it.%20Luckily%2C%20we%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20it%20was%20coming%20out%20fine.%20There%20was%20some%20help%20due%20to%20the%20weather%2C%20so%20very%20happy.%26quot%3B%20Ireland%2C%20however%2C%20took%20India%20to%20cleaners%20in%20the%20back-end%20when%20they%20scored%2054%20runs%20off%20five%20overs%20to%20lift%20them%20to%20a%20respectable%20139%20for%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20every%20game%2C%20you%20would%20want%20more.%20They%20played%20well%2C%20after%20a%20crisis%2C%20they%20played%20well%2C%20credit%20where%20it%20is%20due%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20you%20win%2C%20there%20are%20areas%20to%20improve%20on.%20Everybody%20is%20very%20confident%2C%20they%20are%20very%20well%20prepared.%26quot%3B%20The%20loss%20meant%20Barry%20McCarthy's%2051%20not%20out%20from%2033%20balls%20batting%20at%20No%208%20went%20in%20vain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20nice%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20team.%20Disappointed%20to%20not%20go%20over%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20partnership%20with%20Curtis%20Campher%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20we%20could%20put%20a%20score%20on%20the%20board.%20We%20are%20both%20aggressive%20players%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20playing%20the%20positive%20way%20brings%20the%20game%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20someone%20who%20is%20going%20to%20get%20you%20to%20a%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20the%20game%20to%20the%20opposition%20is%20the%20best%20way.%20Happy%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20team%20no%20matter%20what%20position%20I%20bat%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20signed%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692418140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fim66ua1g_team-india_650x400_18_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fireland-vs-india-2023%2Findia-vs-ireland-not-nervous-but-jasprit-bumrah-first-reaction-after-man-of-the-match-award-on-injury-return-4310249%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Captaining%20a%20second-string%20side%20against%20Ireland%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20led%20India%20to%20a%20two-run%20win%20by%20DLS%20Method%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20three-match%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fireland-vs-india-2023%2Findia-vs-ireland-not-nervous-but-jasprit-bumrah-first-reaction-after-man-of-the-match-award-on-injury-return-4310249%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproje