UK%20court%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ravi%20Jayaram%2C%20from%20the%20Countess%20of%20Chester%20Hospital%20in%20Chester%2C%20said%20some%20of%20those%20lives%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20if%20his%20concerns%20about%20former%20nurse%20colleague%20Lucy%20Letby%20had%20been%20heeded%20and%20the%20police%20alerted%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%2C%2033%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20seven%20newborn%20babies%20and%20also%20found%20guilty%20of%20seven%20counts%20of%20attempted%20murder%20relating%20to%20six%20other%20babies%20by%20a%20jury%20at%20Manchester%20Crown%20Court.%20She%20will%20be%20sentenced%20at%20the%20same%20court%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20genuinely%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20four%20or%20five%20babies%20who%20could%20be%20going%20to%20school%20now%20who%20aren't%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Jayaram%20told%20'ITV%20News'%20in%20a%20television%20interview%20after%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20channel%20that%20consultants%20first%20began%20raising%20concerns%20after%20three%20babies%20died%20in%20June%202015.%20As%20more%20babies%20collapsed%20and%20died%2C%20senior%20medics%20like%20him%20held%20several%20meetings%20with%20hospital%20executives%20to%20raise%20their%20concerns%20about%20Letby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20it%20was%20in%20April%202017%20that%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20trust%20allowed%20doctors%20to%20meet%20with%20a%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%2C%20after%20listening%20to%20us%20for%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%2C%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20something%20that%20they%20had%20to%20be%20involved%20with.%20I%20could%20have%20punched%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Jayaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterwards%2C%20an%20investigation%20was%20launched%20that%20would%20lead%20to%20Letby's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS)%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Letby%20used%20a%20variety%20of%20methods%20to%20secretly%20attack%20a%20total%20of%2013%20babies%20in%20the%20neonatal%20ward%20at%20the%20Countess%20of%20Chester%20hospital%20between%202015%20and%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20trial%2C%20which%20began%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20Manchester%20Crown%20Court%20heard%20that%20doctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20began%20to%20notice%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20babies%20who%20were%20dying%20or%20were%20unexpectedly%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPS%20presented%20evidence%20of%20Letby%20using%20various%20methods%20to%20attack%20babies%2C%20including%20the%20injection%20of%20air%20and%20insulin%20into%20their%20bloodstream%3B%20the%20infusion%20of%20air%20into%20their%20gastrointestinal%20tract%3B%20force%20feeding%20an%20overdose%20of%20milk%20or%20fluids%3B%20impact-type%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20intention%20was%20to%20kill%20the%20babies%20while%20deceiving%20her%20colleagues%20into%20believing%20there%20was%20a%20natural%20cause%2C%20the%20jury%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLucy%20Letby%20sought%20to%20deceive%20her%20colleagues%20and%20pass%20off%20the%20harm%20she%20caused%20as%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20worsening%20of%20each%20baby's%20existing%20vulnerability.%20In%20her%20hands%2C%20innocuous%20substances%20like%20air%2C%20milk%2C%20fluids%20%E2%80%93%20or%20medication%20like%20insulin%20%E2%80%93%20would%20become%20lethal.%20She%20perverted%20her%20learning%20and%20weaponised%20her%20craft%20to%20inflict%20harm%2C%20grief%20and%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pascale%20Jones%20of%20the%20CPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20and%20again%2C%20she%20harmed%20babies%2C%20in%20an%20environment%20which%20should%20have%20been%20safe%20for%20them%20and%20their%20families.%20Her%20attacks%20were%20a%20complete%20betrayal%20of%20the%20trust%20placed%20in%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20was%20first%20arrested%20in%20July%202018%20and%20subsequently%20charged%20in%20November%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Storer%2C%20Chief%20Crown%20Prosecutor%20for%20CPS%20Mersey-Cheshire%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20utterly%20horrifying%20case.%20Like%20everyone%20who%20followed%20the%20trial%2C%20I%20have%20been%20appalled%20by%20Letby's%20callous%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20%E2%80%93%20I%20hope%20your%20unimaginable%20suffering%20is%20eased%20in%20some%20way%20by%20the%20verdicts.%20Our%20thoughts%20remain%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%20Among%20the%20mountain%20of%20evidence%20presented%20in%20court%20were%20many%20handwritten%20notes%20discovered%20by%20police%20during%20their%20investigation.%20They%20included%20phrases%20such%20as%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20killed%20them%20on%20purpose%20because%20I'm%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20care%20for%20them%26quot%3B%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20evil%20I%20did%20this%26quot%3B%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btoday%20is%20your%20birthday%20and%20you%20are%20not%20here%20and%20I%20am%20so%20sorry%20for%20that%26quot%3B.%20These%20notes%20gave%20an%20insight%20into%20Letby's%20mindset%20following%20her%20attacks%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPS%20was%20able%20to%20show%20the%20jury%20that%20Letby%20was%20the%20one%20common%20denominator%20in%20the%20series%20of%20deaths%20and%20sudden%20collapses%20in%20the%20neonatal%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20medical%20documents%20featuring%20falsified%20notes%20made%20by%20the%20nurse%20to%20hide%20her%20involvement%20and%20social%20media%20activity%20to%20deceive%20her%20colleagues%20were%20among%20the%20other%20pieces%20of%20evidence%20presented%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20was%20found%20not%20guilty%20of%20two%20charges%20of%20attempted%20murder%20and%20the%20jury%2C%20many%20of%20them%20visibly%20distraught%20at%20the%20tough%20case%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20reach%20verdicts%20on%20six%20further%20coun