20India%20that%20the%20university%20sent%20a%20detailed%20compliance%20report%20backed%20by%20documentary%20evidence%20before%20the%20deadline%20of%2012%20am%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20the%20three%20who%20were%20arrested%20during%20the%20day%20are%20residents%20of%20Purba%20Bardhaman%2C%20Nadia%20and%20Murshidabad%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20a%20PhD%20course%20from%20a%20private%20institute%20and%20the%20other%20one%20was%20a%20post-graduate%20chemistry%20student.%20The%20third%20one%20is%20a%20fourth-year%20computer%20science%20student%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20summoned%20to%20the%20Jadavpur%20police%20station%20and%20questioned%20during%20the%20day.%20They%20were%20arrested%20as%20their%20replies%20were%20%26quot%3Bincoherent%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20nine%20former%20and%20current%20students%20of%20Jadavpur%20University%20were%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20ragging%20and%20sexually%20harassing%20the%20teenager%20leading%20to%20his%20death%20after%20falling%20from%20a%20second-floor%20balcony%20of%20the%20main%20hostel%20building.%20They%20are%20now%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20on%20Friday%20said%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20campus%2C%20where%20a%20first-year%20undergraduate%20student%20died%20last%20week%20after%20being%20allegedly%20ragged%20and%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20seniors%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20freed%20of%20%26quot%3Banti-national%20elements%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adhikari%2C%20who%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20along%20with%20other%20party%20MLAs%2C%20met%20the%20family%20of%20the%20deceased%20in%20Nadia%20district%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20all%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20with%20the%20family%20and%20will%20help%20them%20in%20whichever%20way%20they%20want.%20What%20has%20happened%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20but%20the%20state%20administration%20cannot%20escape%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adhikari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20ultra-left%20student%20unions%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%2C%20a%20day%20after%20members%20of%20one%20of%20such%20organisations%2C%20All%20India%20Revolutionary%20Students%20Federation%20(AIRSF)%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%20clashed%20outside%20the%20varsity%20where%20Mr%20Adhikari%20had%20gone%20to%20address%20a%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20anti-national%20forces%20need%20to%20be%20ousted%20from%20the%20JU%20campus.%20This%20anarchy%20cannot%20be%20tolerated.%20What%20has%20happened%20is%20completely%20anarchic%20and%20unacceptable.%20Next%20week%20when%20the%20assembly%20session%20resumes%2C%20we%20will%20force%20Education%20Minister%20Bratya%20Basu%20to%20table%20the%20action%20taken%20report%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adhikari%20on%20Friday%20lodged%20a%20police%20complaint%20alleging%20a%20%26quot%3Bpremeditated%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20him%20by%20the%20AIRSF%20workers%20accusing%20them%20of%20being%20a%20part%20of%20a%20group%20that%20made%20JU%20%26quot%3Ba%20den%20of%20anti-national%20and%20anti-social%20activities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20harbour%20anti-establishment%20and%20secessionist%20ideologies%3A%20who%20are%20always%20criticizing%20the%20government%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20clinging%20on%20to%20the%20institution%2C%20even%20after%20their%20formal%20association%20is%20over%2C%20to%20keep%20on%20enjoying%20the%20subsidised%20benefits%20meant%20for%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adhikari%2C%20who%20has%20Z-category%20security%2C%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20he%20was%20suddenly%20attacked%20by%20seven-eight%20people%20as%