23-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentire%20Chinese%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20negatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Fenglish%2Fpressrelease%2F202307%2Ft20230715_1941276.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-gdp-economy-second-quarter-growth-retail-industrial-production-unemployment-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20for%20ages%2016%20-%2024%2C%20employment%20hit%20a%20record%20high%20of%2021.3%25%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20than%20one%20in%205%20people.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trend%20of%20youth%20unemployment%20is%20unmistakable%20because%20NBS'%20own%20data%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20it%20has%20been%20calculated%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20urban%20youth%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20since%202019%20and%20keeps%20growing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sun%20Xin%2C%20a%20lecturer%20at%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20told%20NBC%20News%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESun%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20%26quot%3Bharsh%20business%20environments%26quot%3B%20that%20reduce%20hiring%20in%20foreign%20firms%2C%20while%20the%20state%20sector%20is%20unable%20to%20provide%20enough%20jobs%20that%20fit%20graduates'%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Fenglish%2FPressRelease%2F202308%2Ft20230815_1941964.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuly%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20last%20week%2C%20Chinese%20government%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-july-misses-expectations-no-youth-unemployment-stat-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentirely%20omitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20data%20on%20youth%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20told%20from%20the%20bureau%20told%20%3Ca%20