y%20is%20warning%20the%20domestic%20space%20industry%20of%20the%20growing%20risk%20of%20espionage%20and%20satellite%20attacks%20from%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20other%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20space-related%20companies%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20%26quot%3Bcyberattacks%2C%20strategic%20investment%20(including%20joint%20ventures%20and%20acquisitions)%2C%20the%20targeting%20of%20key%20supply%20chain%20nodes%20and%20other%20techniques%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20space%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20bulletin%20issued%20jointly%20by%20the%20National%20Counterintelligence%20and%20Security%20Center%2C%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%2C%20which%20says%20such%20foreign%20intelligence%20operations%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20company%20secrets%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bdisrupting%20and%20degrading%20US%20satellite%20communications%2C%20remote%20sensing%20and%20imaging%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20comes%20after%20several%20recent%20attacks%20on%20satellites%20and%20mounting%20recognition%20that%20both%20the%20US%20economy%20and%20national%20security%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%20advises%20companies%20to%20log%20anomalies%2C%20establish%20an%20insider-threat%20program%20to%20hunt%20out%20moles%2C%20and%20be%20wary%20of%20requests%20to%20visit%20from%20foreign%20entities%20and%20of%20outreaches%20at%20conferences%20and%20online.%20It%20also%20warns%20about%20%26quot%3Bunsolicited%20offers%20to%20establish%20joint%20ventures%20with%20companies%20tied%20to%20foreign%20governments%20or%20state-owned%20enterprises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20and%20Russia%20historically%20dismiss%20allegations%20that%20they%20have%20carried%20out%20hacking%20and%20other%20attempts%20to%20infiltrate%20or%20disrupt%20space%20systems.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20China's%20embassy%20in%20Washington%20said%20the%20country%20has%20always%20pur