%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBlitzed-Drugs-Third-Norman-Ohler%252Fdp%252F1328663795%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBlitzed%3A%20Drugs%20in%20the%20Third%20Reich%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20studied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2Fbooks%2Fhigh-on-hitler-and-meth-book-says-nazis-were-fueled-by-drugs.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erare%20archival%20documents%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20spoke%20to%20first-hand%20witnesses%20to%20argue%20the%20thesis%20of%20his%202015%20book%3A%20That%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20more%20specifically%2C%20a%20low-dose%20pharmaceutical%20pill%20akin%20to%20modern-day%20meth%20%E2%80%94%20fueled%20the%20Third%20Reich%20and%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20German%20army's%20early-war%20blitzkrieg%20success%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrugs%20have%20often%20played%20a%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohler%20told%20Insider%20of%20wartime%20strategy.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20Nazis%20took%20it%20to%20another%20level%20and%20really%20had%20successes%20because%20of%20the%20drug%20use%2C%20which%20they%20otherwise%20probably%20would%20not%20have%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Third%20Reich%20was%20fueled%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20methamphetamine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmiracle%26quot%3B%20meth%20pill%2C%20as%20Nazi%20Germany%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F5-surprising-times-soldiers-used-performance-enhancing-drugs-meth-cocaine-2023-4%23the-nazis-gave-meth-to-their-soldiers-during-world-war-ii-to-give-them-a-boost-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouted%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%2C%20was%20developed%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20late%201930s%20and%20hit%20the%20market%20as%20Pervitin%2C%20an%20over-the-counter%20pharmaceutical%20that%20quickly%20took%20the%20nation%20by%20storm.%20The%20small%20dosage%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%20about%20three%20milligrams%20of%20modern-day%20meth%2C%20according%20to%20Ohler%2C%20made%20people%20more%20alert%20and%20happier%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPervitin%20was%20already%20popular%20among%20civil%20society%20when%20Dr.%20Otto%20Ranke%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20General%20and%20Defense%20Physiology%2C%20who%20was%20tasked%20with%20improving%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20country's%20soldiers%2C%20began%20to%20envision%20what%20the%20drug%20might%20do%20for%20Germany's%20boys%20headed%20toward%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20decreased%20fear%2C%20increased%20aggression%2C%20reduced%20the%20need%20for%20sleep%2C%20and%20improved%20performance%20of%20simple%20tasks%2C%20Ranke%20found.%20Many%20soldiers%20had%20even%20brought%20it%20with%20them%20when%20the%20war%20started%2C%20Ohler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20it%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20do%20their%20job%2C%20killing%20people%20or%20invading%20a%20foreign%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohler%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adolf%20Hitler%20at%20the%20Western%20Front%20on%20May%2014%2C%201940%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e00879b698ac0019dd1f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221910%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdolf%20Hitler%20at%20the%20Western%20Front%20on%20May%2014%2C%201940%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FHoffman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20were%20stocked%20with%20Pervitin%20as%20the%20drug%20stood%20its%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20real%20military%20test%26quot%3B%20when%20Germany%20invaded%20Poland%20in%201939%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5752114%2Fnazi-military-drugs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20TIME%20report.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20rapid%20overrun%20in%20Poland%20cemented%20Pervitin's%20success%20and%20introduced%20a%20new%20form%20of%20Nazi%20warfare%20known%20as%20blitzkrieg%2C%20which%20was%20characterized%20by%20quick%2C%20surprising%2C%20and%20mechanized%20attacks%20on%20unsuspecting%20enemy%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20enabled%20the%20German%20army%20to%20do%20blitzkrieg%20in%20the%20West.%20They%20didn't%20need%20to%20sleep%20once%20they%20started%20attacking%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohler%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20charging%20through%20France%20and%20Belgium%20and%20Holland%2C%20unafraid%2C%20not%20stopping%2C%20while%20the%20British%20and%20French%20troops%20were%20sleeping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20army%20cited%20Pervitin%20as%20a%20decisive%20factor%20in%20the%20winning%20campaign%2C%20Ohler%20said%2C%20and%20it%20supplied%20its%20troops%20with%20millions%20of%20pills%20ahead%20of%20the%20army's%20attack%20on%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%20Even%20the%20magic%20drug%2C%20however%2C%20could%20not%20win%20Germany%20that%201941%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20dragged%20on%20for%20another%20four%20years%2C%20Pervitin%20continued%20to%20be%20deployed%20to%20soldiers%2C%20Ohler%20said%2C%20but%20the%20one-time%20miracle%20drug%20began%20to%20cause%20dependency%20issues%20and%20depression%20among%20users.%20Germany%20even%20organized%20a%20rehab%20program%20for%20%26quot%3Boverflown%26quot%3B%20pilots%2C%20or%20those%20who%20were%20addicted%20to%20the%20drug%2C%20Ohler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Nazis%20were%20defeated%2C%20production%20of%20Pervitin%20continued%20in%20Germany%2C%20moving%20to%20the%20black%20market%2C%20according%20to%20Ohler.%20Decades%20later%2C%20the%20drug%20was%20used%20by%20East%20German%20border%20troops%20seeking%20to%20stay%20awake%20as%20they%20manned%20the%20Berlin%20Wall%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20drug%20wouldn't%20be%20made%20illegal%20until%20the%201980s%2C%20Ohler%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERampant%20drug%20use%20flew%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Nazi%20ideology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20army's%20dependence%20on%20methamphetamines%20during%20World%20War%20II%20stood%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20Nazi's%20clean-cut%2C%20anti-drug%20image.%20The%20use%20of%20Pervitin%20among%20soldiers%20prompted%20resistance%20from%20high-ranking%20Nazi%20leaders%2C%20who%20were%20concerned%20with%20maintaining%20the%20party's%20ideals%2C%20Ohler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerman%20military%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20were%20focused%20first%20and%20foremost%20on%20trying%20to%20win%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20army%20is%20the%20army.%20In%20the%20field%2C%20it%20has%20to%20fight.%20It%20doesn't%20care%20about%20ideology%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhler%20found%20evidence%20that%20Nazi%20leader%20Adolf%20Hitler%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20soldiers%20were%20using%20Pervitin%2C%20but%20never%20publicly%20acknowledged%20his%20feelings%20toward%20the%20drug.%20The%20dictator%20himself%20was%20abusing%20opioids%20near%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life%2C%20including%20an%20early%20form%20of%20OxyContin%2C%20according%20to%20medical%20records%20reviewed%20by%20Ohler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20other%20militaries%20have%20relied%20on%20chemical%20help%20amid%20wartime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F5-surprising-times-soldiers-used-performance-enhancing-drugs-meth-cocaine-2023-4%23british-stores-sold-syringes-of-heroin-as-gifts-to-send-to-troops-during-world-war-i-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInsider%20reported%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20countries%20have%20a%20history%20of%20supplying%20their%20soldiers%20with%20performance-enhancing%20drugs.%20British%20stores%20used%20to%20sell%20syringes%20of%20heroin%20as%20gifts%20for%20troops%20during%20World%20War%20I%3B%20the%20British%20and%20American%20armies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.mit.edu%2Fjinh%2Farticle-abstract%2F42%2F2%2F205%2F50354%2FMedical-Science-and-the-Military-The-Allies-Use-of%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboth%20relied%20on%20other%20amphetamines%20and%20stimulants%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20after%20witnessing%20the%20drugs'%20success%20for%20the%20Germans%2C%20Ohler%20said%2C%20and%20the%20US%20military%20distributed%20painkillers%20and%20%26quot%3Bpep%20pills%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20speed%20%E2%80%94%20to%20soldiers%20headed%20toward%20long-range%20reconnaissance%20missions%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlcohol%20has%20also%20been%20a%20common%20battle%20bedfellow%20throughout%20history.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-vodka-historian-sees-parallels-between-now-and-past-wars-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20military%20gave%20its%20soldiers%20vodka%20rations%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20through%20World%20War%20II%3B%20France%20opted%20for%20red%20wine%3B%20and%20alcohol%20remained%20the%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20one%26quot%3B%20drug%20for%20Germans%20during%20the%20war%2C%20Ohler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20life-or-death%20stakes%20of%20war%2C%20performance-enhancing%20drugs%2C%20despite%20their%20numerous%20and%20notable%20downsides%2C%20maybe%20too%20enticing%20a%20boost%20to%20pass%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20drugs%20were%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20used%20in%20the%20Ukrainian-Russian%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohler%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20too%20good%20for%20an%20army.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-high-amphetamines-ukraine-nazis-third-reich-drugs-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692410780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e007fbb698ac0019dd1ec1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-high-amphetamines-ukraine-nazis-third-reich-drugs-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drugs%20