ntists%20can't%20attribute%20any%20single%20event%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-army-sediment-cores-greenland-melted-past-climate-change-sea-level-2023-7%5C%22%3Eclimate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20assessing%20it%20on%20its%20own.%20But%20local%20researchers%20have%20been%20warning%20for%20years%20that%20hotter%2C%20drier%20conditions%20were%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20big%20fires%20on%20Maui.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222420%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20flames%20as%20wildfires%20engulfed%20the%20historic%20town%20of%20Lahaina%2C%20Maui%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20U.S.%20August%209%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d8e1af1f51cc001968773f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlames%20seen%20as%20wildfires%20engulfed%20the%20historic%20town%20of%20Lahaina%2C%20Maui%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20U.S.%3Cp%3EErin%20Hawk%2FHandout%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20burn%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20oil%20for%20energy%2C%20that%20emits%20gases%20into%20the%20atmosphere%20that%20trap%20heat.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20global%20temperatures%20are%20rising.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20that's%20fueling%20droughts%20and%20wildfires.%20That's%20because%20a%20warmer%20atmosphere%20sucks%20more%20moisture%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20its%20vegetation%2C%20creating%20more%20fuel%20for%20blazes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDroughts%20and%20fires%20are%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20but%20they're%20getting%20much%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20seeing%20a%20pretty%20steady%20increase%2C%20and%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20an%20exponential%20increase%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20area%20that%20burns%20in%20Hawaii%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Abby%20Frazier%2C%20a%20climatologist%20at%20Clark%20University%2C%20told%20Nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20image%20taken%20on%20August%2010%2C%202023%20shows%20destroyed%20homes%20and%20buildings%20burned%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20Lahaina%20on%20Hawaii's%20Maui%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d676fd1f51cc0019680422%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20image%20taken%20shows%20destroyed%20homes%20and%20buildings%20burned%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20Lahaina%20on%20Hawaii's%20Maui%20island.%3Cp%3EPATRICK%20T.%20FALLON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrush%20fires%20and%20their%20resulting%20complications%20have%20become%20more%20common%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mauicounty.gov%2FDocumentCenter%2FView%2F129493%2FReport-on-Wildfire-Prevention--Cost-Recovery-on-Maui---Part-1-Report--Exhibits-A-B-33-MB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202021%20report%20by%20Maui%20County%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20%26quot%3BThis%20increase%20poses%20an%20increased%20threat%20to%20citizens%2C%20properties%2C%20and%20sacred%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20detailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBad%20luck%3A%20Hurricane%20Dora%20made%20strong%20winds%20that%20whipped%20fire%20into%20a%20frenzy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHurricane%20Dora%20didn't%20hit%20Hawaii%2C%20but%20its%20passing%20created%20powerful%20winds%20that%20helped%20spread%20the%20fire%20farther%2C%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaui%20was%20caught%20between%20a%20high-pressure%20system%20to%20the%20north%20and%20the%20hurricane%2C%20which%20is%20a%20low-pressure%20system%2C%20to%20the%20south.%20Because%20these%20systems%20were%20so%20close%20together%20and%20their%20pressures%20were%20so%20different%2C%20trade%20winds%20grew%20strong%20as%20they%20moved%20between%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F10%2Fus%2Fmaui-wildfires-cause-hawaii.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20New%20York%20Times%20meteorologist%20Judson%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20Maui%20reported%20wind%20gusts%20of%20up%20to%2067%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20and%20flames%20rise%20in%20Lahaina%2C%20Maui%20County%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20U.S.%2C%20August%208%2C%202023%20in%20this%20still%20image%20from%20video%20obtained%20from%20social%20media.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d51157005c4a00183d3c79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20and%20flames%20rise%20in%20Lahaina%2C%20Maui%20County%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20U.S.%2C%20August%208%2C%202023%20in%20this%20still%20image%20from%20video%20obtained%20from%20social%20media.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Melichar%2FTMX%2Fvia%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20study%20has%20been%20conducted%20to%20assess%20Hurricane%20Dora's%20relationship%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20but%20on%20the%20whole%20scientists%20know%20that%20rising%20global%20temperatures%20can%20increase%20the%20strength%20%E2%80%94%20aka%20the%20wind%20speed%20%E2%80%94%20of%20hurricanes.%20That's%20because%20the%20storms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-causes-hurricanes-irma-harvey-jose-sahara-africa-easterly-atlantic-2017-9%5C%22%3Efeed%20on%20warm%20water%20and%20warm%20air%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMismanagement%20or%20system%20failures%3A%20No%20sirens%2C%20no%20warning%2C%20no%20water%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20officials%20knew%20about%20the%20mounting%20risk%20fires%20posed%20to%20Maui%2C%20their%20warning%20systems%20were%20woefully%20insufficient.%20The%20sirens%20didn't%20go%20off%2C%20the%20evacuation%20orders%20were%20late%2C%20and%20the%20water%20hydrants%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20recent%20test%20of%20the%20sirens%20on%20August%201st%2C%20there%20were%20issues%20with%20them%20in%20three%20counties%2C%20%3Ca%20re