to%20ragging%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20three%20more%20persons%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20arrests%20in%20the%20case%20stands%20at%2012%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadavpur%20University%20(JU)%20authorities%20has%20rolled%20out%20various%20measures%2C%20including%20making%20identity%20cards%20mandatory%20for%20visitors%20to%20enter%20the%20campus%20at%20night%20and%20installing%20CCTVs%20at%20strategic%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20circular%20issued%20on%20Thursday%2C%20identity%20cards%20issued%20by%20the%20university%20will%20be%20mandatory%20for%20entering%20the%20campus%20from%208%20pm%20to%207%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20authorities%2C%20this%20would%20help%20curb%20the%20entry%20of%20outsiders%20to%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20individuals%20who%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20University%20campus%20between%208.00%20PM%20to%207%3A00%20AM%20will%20have%20to%20carry%20valid%20Identity%20Card(s)%20issued%20by%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadavpur%20University.%20It%20will%20have%20to%20be%20produced%20on%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20a%20person%20does%20not%20have%20an%20ID%20card%20issued%20by%20the%20university%2C%20he%20or%20she%20will%20have%20to%20produce%20some%20other%20valid%20proof%20of%20identity%20and%20enter%20the%20details%20of%20the%20person%2C%20where%20he%20or%20she%20is%20going%20to%20meet%20in%20a%20register%20kept%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20vehicles%2C%20including%20two-wheelers%20entering%20the%20campus%2C%20will%20have%20to%20now%20bear%20stickers%20issued%20by%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo-wheelers%20or%20four-wheelers%20must%20have%20a%20JU%20sticker%20issued%20by%20the%20University.%20The%20Vehicles%20without%20JU%20stickers%20must%20provide%20their%2