3EMint%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECisco%20CEO%20surprised%20analysts%20by%20mentioning%20it%20had%20already%20sold%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%20of%20AI%20gear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECisco%20is%20trying%20to%20woo%20cloud%20companies%20away%20from%20offerings%20by%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20analyst%20says%20it's%20a%20promising%20start%20on%20a%20potentially%20huge%20new%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20CEO%20Chuck%20Robbins%20dropped%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20bombshell%20during%20its%20earnings%20conference%20call%20Wednesday.%20That's%20when%20he%20told%20analysts%20the%20company%20had%20already%20sold%20over%20%24500%20million%20worth%20of%20equipment%20to%20the%20largest%20cloud%20computing%20companies%20for%20their%20AI%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cloud%20companies%20(or%20hyperscalers%20as%20the%20tech%20world%20calls%20them)%20are%20buying%20from%20Cisco%20because%20they%20are%20experimenting%20with%20using%20Ethernet%20%E2%80%94%20the%20networking%20technology%20that%20Cisco%20is%20known%20for%20%E2%80%94%20for%20their%20AI%20needs%20instead%20of%20Infiniband.%20Infiniband%20is%20the%20high-speed%20networking%20technology%20more%20typically%20used%20by%20data%20centers%2C%20a%20market%20cornered%20by%20Nvidia%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmellanox-technologies-nvidia-to-buy-in-69-billion-deal-2019-3-1028018625%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20bought%20leader%20Mellanox%20Technologies%20in%20a%20%246.9%20billion%20in%202019.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Cisco%2C%20along%20with%20AMD%2C%20Arista%2C%20Broadcom%2C%20HPE%2C%20Intel%2C%20Meta%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20formed%20a%20technology%20coalition%20last%20month%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fleading-cloud-service-semiconductor-and-system-providers-unite-to-form-ultra-ethernet-consortium-301880208.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_