ned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20now%20are%20installed%20in%2021%20use%20cases%20across%20the%20top%20six%20of%20these%20providers.%20And%20we%20expect%20that%20that%20momentum%20will%20just%20continue%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20analyst%20Meta%20Marshall%20is%20intrigued%20but%20cautiously%20skeptical.%20In%20a%20post-earnings%20research%20note%2C%20she%20pointed%20out%20that%20there's%20%26quot%3Ban%20intense%20investor%20focus%26quot%3B%20on%20companies%20positioned%20for%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20build-out%20and%20Cisco's%20investors%20want%20to%20hear%20its%20AI%20story.%20After%20all%2C%20at%20about%20a%20%24225%20billion%20market%20cap%2C%20Cisco's%20valuation%20is%20one-quarter's%20of%20Nvidia's%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%24500%20million%20sold%20so%20far%20is%20currently%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20in%20terms%20of%20revenue%2C%20growing%20relevancy%20within%20this%20customer%20base%20is%20important%2C%20particularly%20given%20scale%20of%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20still%20think%20Cisco%20has%20smaller%20share%20within%20these%20hyperscalers%2C%20increasing%20penetration%20is%20a%20positive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20Cisco%20employee%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20Julie%20Bort%20through%20email%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajbort%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ejbort%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20encrypted%20chat%20app%20Signal%20at%20970-430-6112%20or%20DM%20on%20Twitter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJulie188%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%40julie188%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20using%20a%20non-work%20devic%3C%2Fem%3Ee.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%