mandate-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Insider%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20initially%20revealed%20to%20workers%20in%20June%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20have%20people%20back%20in%20the%20office%20this%20year%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20guidelines%20issued%20Thursday%2C%20Meta%20made%20clear%20that%20office%20attendance%20is%20strictly%20mandatory%20for%20everyone%20that%20is%20not%20approved%20for%20fully%20remote%20work.%20Workers%20need%20to%20be%20in%20their%20assigned%20offices%20most%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20be%20monitored%20by%20their%20managers%20and%20have%20attendance%20tracked%20by%20the%20company.%20Those%20who%20flout%20the%20new%20rules%20risk%20%26quot%3Btermination%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20being%20fired%2C%20Goler's%20note%20said.%20It%20could%20also%20impact%20their%20performance%20reviews%2C%20which%20have%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-doubles-target-lowest-performance-ratings-non-regrettable-attrition-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20harsher%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20RTO%20policy%20is%20now%20as%20stringent%20as%20Amazon's%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-stirs-employees-anxiety-with-rushed-return-to-office-plan-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Every%20firm%20stance%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20people%20returning%20to%20the%20office.%20Under%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%2C%20Amazon%20is%20also%20forcing%20people%20back%20to%20work%20in%20their%20assigned%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20despite%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-executive-no-data-to-support-return-to-office-mandate-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eno%20data%20to%20back%20up%20the%20move%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Google%20has%20also%20said%20staff%20who%20don't%20work%20in-office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20could%20see%20their%20performance%20reviews%20impacted%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-crackdown-on-remote-work-rto-frustrates-employees-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20move%20that%20has%20frustrated%20many%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20himself%20this%20year%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20more%20hardened%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mark-zuckerberg-meta-facebook-ceo-layoffs-profit-cage-match-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWall%20Street-appeasing%20CEO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20public%20discussion%20of%20the%20metaverse%20has%20turned%20away%20from%20an%20initial%20desire%20for%20his%20ambitious%20virtual%20world%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerweekly.com%2Fnews%2F252525977%2FMeta-presents-vision-for-business-metaverse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enew%20era%20of%20remote%20work%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20still%20allowing%20employees%20hired%20in%20fully%20remote%20roles%2C%20or%20those%20already%20approved%20for%20fully%20remote%20work%2C%20to%20continue%20working%20that%20way.%20Anyone%20else%20who%20wishes%20to%20work%20remotely%20will%20need%20to%20formally%20apply%20and%20be%20approved%2C%20with%20considerations%20including%20how%20long%20they've%20worked%20at%20the%20company%20and%20their%20performance%20reviews.%20No%20one%20with%20less%20than%2018%20months%20tenure%20at%20Meta%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20work%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20fucking%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20current%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20guidelines%20appear%20to%20be%20tailored%20specifically%20to%20avoid%20remote%20workers%20having%20their%20cake%2C%20and%20eating%20it%2C%20too.%20Literally.%20Employees%20who%20are%20fully%20remote%20can%20only%20come%20into%20the%20office%2C%20which%20includes%20access%20to%20Meta's%20cafeteria%20and%20catered%20meals%2C%20a%20few%20days%20each%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESee%20below%20for%20a%20complete%20list%20of%20Meta's%20new%20rules%20for%20in-office%20and%20remote%20work%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E-Starting%20September%205%2C%20all%20employees%20with%20an%20assigned%20office%20are%20required%20to%20work%20in%20an%20office%20or%20%26quot%3Bin%20person%26quot%3B%20at%20least%20three%20days%20each%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-In-person%20work%20can%20include%20things%20like%20meetings%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Meanwhile%2C%20employees%20already%20approved%20for%20remote%20work%20are%20prohibited%20from%20coming%20into%20an%20office%20more%20than%20four%20days%20every%20two%20months%20outside%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20business%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20a%20company%20onsite%20event%20or%20a%20mandatory%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Some%20leaders%20of%20individual%20orgs%20and%20teams%20within%20Meta%20will%20be%20able%20to%20decide%20which%20days%20of%20the%20week%20are%20'preferred'%20for%20in-office%20work%2C%20or%20an%20%26quot%3Borg-specific%20location%20strategy.%26quot%3B%20That%20process%20is%20ongoing.%20Employees%20are%20expected%20to%20adhere%20to%20any%20such%20set%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-A%20remote%20employee%20who%20is%20working%20in%20a%20location%20that%20ends%20up%20outside%20of%20an%20orgs%20location%20strategy%20will%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20relocate.%20Org%20location%20strategy%20will%20be%20used%20to%20guide%20future%20hiring%20and%20transfer%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Remote%20work%20overall%20will%20be%20limited%20to%20%26quot%3Brare%2C%20approved%20candidate%20exceptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Meta%20will%20be%20tracking%20data%20from%20employees'%20badges%2C%20or%20the%20ID%20cards%20used%20to%20enter%20and%20exit%20offices%20and%20certain%20areas%20within%20offices%2C%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20the%20RTO%20and%20remote%20work%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Managers%20will%20be%20tracking%20employees'%20%26quot%3Bbadge%20data.%26quot%3B%20Managers%20will%20also%20be%20tracking%20each%20employee's%20Status%20Tool%2C%20an%20internal%20tool%20for%20employees%20to%20display%20where%20they%20are%20working%2C%20which%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20be%20updated%20at%20all%20times.%20Both%20will%20be%20evaluated%20monthly%2C%20for%20in-office%20and%20remote%20workers%2C%20and%20employees%20found%20to%20be%20non-compliant%20will%20be%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-If%20an%20employee%20is%20found%20to%20be%20not%20following%20the%20RTO%20rules%2C%20it%20will%20likely%20impact%20their%20twice-yearly%20performance%20evaluation%20and%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20disciplinary%20action%20or%20termination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Meta%20employee%20or%20someone%20else%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akhays%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekhays%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20on%20secure%20messaging%20app%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ESignal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20Twitter%20DM%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHaysKali%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%40hayskali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20non-work%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReach%20out%20to%20Hugh%20Langley%20via%20encrypted%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40protonmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehlangley%40protonmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E)%20or%20encrypted%20messaging%20apps%20Signal%2FTelegram%20(%2B1%20628-228-1836).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%