%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fsage-steele-barbara-walters-assault-attack-the-view-1235699926%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lucy%20Letby%3A%20From%20Nurse%20To%20Child%20Murderer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20of%20nurse%20Lucy%20Letby%2C%20who%20was%20on%20Friday%20found%20guilty%20of%20murdering%20seven%20babies%20and%20attempting%20to%20kill%20another%20six%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20in%20British%20criminal%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucy%20Letby%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Hereford%20in%20western%20England%2C%20Letby%20studied%20nursing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chester.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Manchester%20Crown%20Court%20during%20her%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20graduated%20in%202011%20and%20started%20full-time%20at%20the%20Countess%20of%20Chester%20Hospital%20the%20following%20year%2C%20joining%20the%20neo-natal%20unit.%20%C2%A0In%202015%2C%20she%20qualified%20to%20work%20on%20intensive%20care%20babies%2C%20which%20would%20have%20allowed%20her%20to%20work%20with%20the%20sickest%20babies%20in%20the%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20an%20active%20social%20life%2C%20attended%20salsa%20classes%2C%20travelled%20and%20went%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20the%20court%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVictims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20was%20accused%20of%20harming%2017%20babies%2C%20some%20of%20them%20just%20days%20old%2C%20between%20June%202015%20and%20June%202016.%20In%20the%20majority%20of%20cases%20she%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20injected%20them%20with%20air%20but%20prosecutors%20also%20accused%20her%20of%20introducing%20insulin%20or%20too%20much%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20found%20her%20guilty%20of%20murdering%20seven%20babies%20and%20attempting%20to%20kill%20six%20others%20on%20the%2022nd%20day%20of%20deliberations.%20She%20was%20found%20not%20guilty%20on%20two%20counts%20of%20attempted%20murder%20and%20the%20jury%20could%20not%20reach%20a%20verdict%20on%20six%20attempted%20murder%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20her%20victims%20were%20a%20twin%20brother%20and%20sister%20and%20two%20triplet%20boys.%20The%20names%20of%20the%20babies%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20be%20reported%20and%20are%20instead%20referred%20to%20as%20baby%20A%20through%20to%20Q.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20is%20said%20to%20have%20on%20several%20occasions%20carried%20out%20Facebook%20searches%20for%20the%20parents%20of%20babies%20that%20she%20allegedly%20attacked.%20She%20said%20she%20would%20look%20up%20to%20people%20when%20she%20was%20thinking%20about%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuspicion%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neo-natal%20unit%20saw%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20babies%20dying%20and%20suffering%20serious%20collapses%20during%20the%20period%20in%20question%2C%20prosecutor%20Nick%20Johnson%20said%20at%20the%20trial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20for%20the%20cause%20revealed%20%26quot%3Bone%20common%20denominator%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20was%20Letby%2C%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0Following%20the%20deaths%20of%20two%20triplets%20in%20June%202016%2C%20Letby%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20neo-natal%20unit%20and%20placed%20on%20clerical%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20life-changing%2C%20in%20that%20moment%20I%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20the%20support%20system%20I%20had%20on%20the%20unit%2C%20I%20was%20put%20in%20a%20role%20I%20did%20not%20enjoy%20and%20I%20had%20to%20pretend%20it%20was%20voluntary%2C%26quot%3B%20Letby%20told%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Royal%20College%20of%20Nursing%20that%20blamed%20her%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20babies.%20She%20told%20the%20court%20she%20was%20prescribed%20anti-depressants%2C%20which%20she%20is%20still%20taking%2C%20and%20admitted%20to%20having%20thoughts%20of%20harming%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrests%20And%20Search%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20was%20arrested%20and%20released%20twice%2C%20with%20her%20first%20arrest%20in%20July%202018.%20On%20her%20third%20arrest%20in%202020%2C%20she%20was%20formally%20charged%20and%20placed%20into%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20items%20found%20during%20a%20search%20of%20Letby's%20home%20was%20a%20Post-it%20note%20on%20which%20she%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20deserve%20to%20live.%20I%20killed%20them%20on%20purpose%20because%20I'm%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20care%20for%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20evil%20I%20did%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20capital%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20claimed%20the%20note%20was%20written%20around%20the%20time%20she%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20neo-natal%20unit%2C%20leaving%20her%20feeling%20like%20she%20%26quot%3Bhad%20done%20something%20wrong%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20said%20police%20also%20found%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge%20quantity%26quot%3B%20of%20hospital%20paperwork%20relating%20to%20several%20of%20the%20children%20that%20she%20is%20accused%20of%20harming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetby's%20Defence%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresenting%20Letby%2C%20lawyer%20Ben%20Myers%20said%20it's%20important%20that%20%26quot%3Bblame%20is%20not%20heaped%20on%20that%20woman%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20there%20may%20be%20others%20who%20made%20mistakes%20or%20systems%20that%20had%20failed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20Letby%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdedicated%20nurse%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bcared%20deeply%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20babies%20and%20their%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Myers%20also%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20direct%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20Letby%20committing%20the%20crimes%20and%20pointed%20to%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20babies%20at%20birth%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bclinically%20fragile%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20unit%20had%20staffing%20issues%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20hurting%20or%20wanting%20to%20hurt%20the%20babies%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20completely%20against%20what%20being%20a%20nurse%20is%26quot%3B.%20She%20had%20suggested%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bgang%26quot%3B%20of%20four%20hospital%20consultants%20had%20conspired%20to%20pin%20the%20blame%20on%20her%20%26quot%3Bto%20cover%20failings%20at%20the%20hospital%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692385020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fofmn7ano_letby-was-accused-of-harming-17-babies_625x300_18_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flucy-letby-from-nurse-to-child-murderer-4309987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Letby%20was%20accused%20of%20harming%2017%20babies%2C%20some%20of%20them%20just%20days%20old%2C%20between%20June%202015%20and%20June%202016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flucy-letby-from-nurse-to-child-murderer-4309987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flucy-letby-from-nurse-to-child-murderer-4309987%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flucy-letby-from-nurse-to-child-murderer-4309987%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%2C%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20condemn%20'dangerous%20and%20aggressive%20actions'%20by%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2