ffering%20new%20insight%20into%20ninth%20century%20burial%20rituals%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20presence%20of%20Christianity%20in%20the%20country%20at%20the%20time%2C%20church%20cemeteries%20were%20not%20yet%20the%20norm%20in%209th%20century%20England%2C%20and%20there%20were%20few%20uniform%20burial%20customs%20during%20the%20period%2C%20the%20museum%20said.%20But%20one%20commonality%20that%20does%20exist%20among%20the%20majority%20of%20burials%20from%20that%20period%20is%20the%20position%20of%20the%20body%20being%20face-up%2C%20the%20museum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologists%2C%20however%2C%20discovered%20the%20Conington%20girl%20buried%20face-down%20in%20a%20pit%20that%20marked%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20small%20settlement%20and%20believe%20her%20ankles%20may%20have%20also%20been%20tied%20together%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MOLA%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20well%20as%20being%20buried%20face%20down%20on%20a%20boundary%2C%20the%20position%20of%20her%20ankles%20suggests%20they%20may%20have%20been%20tied%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20MOLA%20senior%20human%20osteologist%20Don%20Walker%20said%20in%20a%20museum%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20implies%20that%20the%20community%20took%20extra%20measures%20to%20ensure%20she%20could%20not%20'return'%20from%20the%20grave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2211780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20early%20Medieval%20community%20at%20Conington.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64de9f47b698ac0019dbd760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225102%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20early%20Medieval%20community%20at%20Conington.%3Cp%3EOxford%20Archaeology%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finding%20calls%20to%20mind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-find-vampire-child-padlocked-in-polish-graveyard-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b