dware%20they're%20using.%20GeForce%20Now%20even%20offers%20its%20own%20downloadable%20cloud%20gaming%20app%2C%20which%20is%20rare%20for%20Chromebooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20play%20a%20cloud%20game%2C%20the%20game%20actually%20runs%20on%20a%20powerful%20computer%20off%20in%20a%20server%20farm%20somewhere.%20The%20image%20you%20see%20is%20a%20video%20being%20streamed%20from%20that%20computer%20to%20your%20screen.%20The%20only%20things%20you%20need%20are%20an%20internet%20connection%20to%20receive%20the%20video%2C%20and%20a%20keyboard%20or%20controller%20to%20send%20your%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20best%20way%20to%20play%20new%2C%20high-end%20games%20on%20a%20Chromebook.%20This%20includes%20titles%20like%20Fortnite%2C%20Valorant%2C%20Overwatch%2C%20Minecraft%2C%20Forza%20Horizon%205%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nigh%20countless%20number%20of%20great%20games%2C%20with%20more%20being%20added%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20game%20Guilty%20Gear%20Strive%20running%20on%20a%20Chromebook%20using%20Xbox%20Cloud%20Gaming.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df742ab698ac0019dc333f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20cloud%20gaming%20services%2C%20you%20can%20run%20games%20that%20your%20Chromebook%20normally%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20handle.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3B%20Microsoft%3B%20Arc%20System%20Works%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECloud%20gaming%20does%20have%20its%20downsides.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20consistently%20stable%20and%20fast%20internet%20connection%2C%20your%20games%20can%20lag%2C%20stutter%2C%20and%20suffer%20from%20visual%20glitches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20cloud%20gaming%20also%20requires%20a%20monthly%20subscription%2C%20which%20costs%20money.%20Xbox%20Game%20Pass'%20Cloud%20Gaming%20feature%20requires%20an%20%26quot%3BUltimate'%20subscription%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%2417%20a%20month.%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20Now%20and%20Amazon%20Luna%20both%20start%20at%20%2410%20per%20month%2C%20although%20GeForce%20Now%20also%20offers%20a%20free%20tier%20that%20only%20lets%20you%20play%20for%20one%20hour%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Web%20browser%20games%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20Google%20Chrome%20to%20play%20web%20browser%20games%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20check%20out%20browser%20games%2C%20which%20can%20offer%20hours%20of%20fun%20even%20on%20the%20weakest%20computers.%20There%20are%20dozens%20of%20websites%20that%20you%20can%20play%20free%20browser%20games%20on%2C%20but%20the%20three%20best%20are%20Itch.io%2C%20the%20Internet%20Archive%2C%20and%20Newgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitch.io%2Fgames%2Ftop-sellers%2Fplatform-web%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItch.io%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20online%20database%20and%20marketplace%20for%20new%20indie%20games.%20As%20of%20this%20writing%2C%20the%20site%20offers%20over%20350%2C000%20games%20that%20you%20can%20play%20entirely%20within%20your%20browser%2C%20no%20downloads%20required.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20Archive%3C%2Fa%3E%20features%20a%20built-in%20emulator%20that%20lets%20you%20play%20hundreds%20of%20classic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fsoftwarelibrary_msdos_games%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMS-DOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Finternetarcade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earcade%3C%2Fa%3E%20games%20in%20your%20browser.%20And%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newgrounds.com%2Fgames%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20website%20for%20quick%20and%20fun%20flash%20games%2C%20along%20with%20short%20movies%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20visual%20art%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Android%20apps%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store%20to%20play%20Android%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Chromebooks%20have%20a%20dedicated%20Google%20Play%20Store%20app%20which%20lets%20you%20download%20and%20play%20almost%20any%20Android%20app.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20favorite%20mobile%20app%20%E2%80%94%20Genshin%20Impact%2C%20Crossy%20Road%2C%20Yu-Gi-Oh%3A%20Duel%20Links%20%E2%80%94%20chances%20are%20you%20can%20run%20it%20on%20your%20Chromebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221918%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store%20information%20page%20for%20the%20game%20Yu-Gi-Oh%3A%20Duel%20Links%2C%20and%20that%20game%20playing%20alongside%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df7325bd98a6001979007b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221438%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20run%20nearly%20any%20Android%20game%2C%20and%20use%20your%20mouse%20in%20place%20of%20your%20finger.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3B%20Google%3B%20Konami%20Digital%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Play%20Store%20should%20be%20enabled%20by%20default%20on%20compatible%20Chromebooks.%20But%20if%20it's%20not%2C%20you%20can%20open%20the%20Settings%20menu%20and%20scroll%20down%20to%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EApps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20or%20%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20Play%20Store%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20section%20to%20enable%20it.%20Just%20note%20that%20if%20your%20Google%20account%20is%20managed%20by%20an%20outside%20administrator%2C%20like%20your%20work%20or%20school%2C%20the%20Play%20Store%20might%20be%20permanently%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Play%20Store%20also%20isn't%20available%20on%20all%20Chromebook%20models.%20Check%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fchromebook%2Fanswer%2F7021273%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20support%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20if%20your%20Chromebook%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B%20Play%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Linux%20games%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20Chromebooks%20can%20also%20run%20Linux%20games%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EChromebooks%20run%20on%20an%20operating%20system%20(OS)%20called%20Chrome%20OS%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20a%20more%20common%20OS%20called%20Linux.%20And%20although%20game%20developers%20don't%20usually%20make%20games%20for%20Chromebooks%2C%20they%20%3Cem%3Edo%3C%2Fem%3E%20make%20games%20for%20Linux%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they%20can%20probably%20run%20on%20your%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20Chromebook%20was%20made%20in%202019%20or%20later%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20Linux%20pre-installed.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20enable%20it.%20If%20your%20Chromebook%20was%20made%20earlier%20than%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fa%2Fchromium.org%2Fdev%2Fchromium-os%2Fchrome-os-systems-supporting-linux%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeck%20this%20list%20to%20see%20whether%20it%20includes%20Linux%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it's%20not%20on%20the%20list%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20install%20it%20from%20the%20internet%20or%20a%20USB%20flash%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20enable%20Linux%2C%20open%20your%20Chromebook's%20Settings%20app%2C%20click%20%3Cstrong%3EAdvanced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20then%20find%20the%20%3Cstrong%3ELinux%20development%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20section%20and%20click%20%3Cstrong%3ETurn%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Use%20the%20menus%20that%20open%20to%20turn%20on%20Linux.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222597%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Linux%20options%20in%20a%20Chromebook%E2%80%99s%20Settings%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df7214bd98a6001978ff84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20turn%20on%20your%20Chromebook%E2%80%99s%20Linux%20options%20through%20this%20menu.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3B%20Google%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20it's%20enabled%2C%20you'll%20have%20access%20to%20the%20Terminal%20app.%20You%20can%20then%20use%20the%20Terminal%20to%20install%20new%20apps%2C%20including%20Steam%2C%20the%20popular%20game%20launcher%20that%20maintains%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Flinux%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20own%20Linux%20section%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20gives%20you%20access%20to%20thousands%20of%20new%20games%2C%20including%20popular%20titles%20like%20Counter-Strike%3A%20Global%20Offensive%2C%20Dota%202%2C%20and%20Cities%3A%20Skylines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20remember%20that%20although%20you're%20using%20a%20new%20OS%2C%20you're%20still%20limited%20to%20the%20same%20hardware.%20Graphically%20intensive%20Steam%20games%20probably%20won't%20work%2C%20and%20you'll%20need%20to%20lower%20the%20visual%20settings%20on%20others.%20And%20if%20your%20Chromebook's%20graphics%20card%20isn't%20powerful%20enough%20to%20run%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20games%2C%20enabling%20Linux%20won't%20help%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20their%20PC%20(or%20even%20Mac)%20counterparts%2C%20Chromebooks%20definitely%20don't%20make%20for%20great%20gaming%20laptops.%20They%20have%20underpowered%20graphics%20cards%2C%20and%20don't%20support%20the%20same%20kinds%20of%20apps%20as%20other%20computers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBut%20if%20you%20take%20advantage%20of%20what%20Chrome%20OS%20does%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stable%20internet%20browser%2C%20Android%20support%2C%20Linux%20architecture%20%E2%80%94%20you%2