on%20to%20remit%20their%20life%20sentence%20and%20set%20aside%20recommendations%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20concerned%20are%2011%20men%20who%20gangraped%20a%20pregnant%2019-year-old%20Bano%20and%20killed%20her%20relatives%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20trial%20was%20transferred%20to%20a%20court%20in%20neighbouring%20Maharashtra%20state%2C%20the%2011%20men%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%20prison%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifteen%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20was%20up%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-bilkis-case-remissions-8094290%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20decide%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20to%20release%20the%20men%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20state%20government%20release%20them%20from%20prison%20after%20considering%20the%20remission%20policy%20that%20was%20in%20force%20at%20the%20time%20they%20committed%20their%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20(August%2017)%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%20argued%20that%20even%20those%20who%20committed%20heinous%20crimes%20such%20as%20the%20accused%20in%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20case%20have%20a%20right%20to%20rehabilitate%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20put%20the%20following%20questions%20to%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20the%20purpose%20of%20remission%20punishment%3F%20Does%20committing%20a%20heinous%20crime%20debar%20a%20convict%20from%20getting%20its%20benefit%2C%20even%20if%20the%20convict%20has%20reformed%20themselves%2C%20has%20displayed%20remorse%20and%20wants%20to%20start%20a%20new%20life%20again%3F%20Should%20the%20past%20always%20be%20dangling%20above%20your%20head%3F%20Should%20these%20convicts%20be%20condemned%20for%20all%20times%20to%20come%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-bilkis-bano-reformation-remission-policy-being-selectively-applied-235468%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funderstanding-the-remission-policy-that-led-to-the-release-of-bilkis-banos-rapists%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20Remission%20Policy%20That%20Led%20to%20the%20Release%20of%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20Rapists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20men%20were%20not%20given%20the%20death%20penalty%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20there%20was%20scope%20for%20their%20reformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20law%20does%20not%20say%20that%20every%20convict%20should%20be%20hanged%2C%20or%20even%20punished%20perpetually%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20law%20speaks%20about%20giving%20a%20chance%20to%20even%20the%20most%20hardened%20criminal%20to%20reform%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20doubted%20this%20was%20the%20only%20reason%20why%20these%2011%20men%20were%20given%20a%20remission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20far%20is%20this%20law%20being%20applied%20to%20inmates%20in%20jail%3F%20Why%20are%20our%20jails%20overcrowded%3F%20Particularly%20with%20undertrials%3F%20Why%20is%20the%20policy%20of%20remission%20being%20applied%20selectively%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20raised%20this%20question%20again%20during%20another%20point%20in%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20how%20far%20is%20the%20remission%20policy%20being%20implemented%20in%20cases%20where%20convicts%20have%20completed%2014%20years%3F%20Is%20remission%20policy%20being%20implemented%20in%20all%20such%20cases%2C%20subject%20of%20course%20to%20their%20eligibility%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20agreed%20that%20all%20eligible%20convicts%20must%20be%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20rehabilitate%20themselves%2C%20but%20said%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20statistics%20to%20answer%20Justice%20Nagarathna%E2%80%99s%20question%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20facts%20of%20a%20case%2C%20I%20may%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20%E2%80%A6%20you%20will%20have%20to%20have%20the%20statistics.%20The%20state-wise%20statistics.%20The%20opportunity%20to%20reform%20should%20be%20given%20to%20every%20prisoner.%20Not%20only%20to%20a%20few%20prisoners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24173232%2FAhmedabad_riots1-1024x692.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24173232%2FAhmedabad_riots1-1024x692.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24173232%2FAhmedabad_riots1-300x203.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24173232%2FAhmedabad_riots1.jpg%201184w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637477%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22568%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBano%E2%80%99s%20three-year-old%20daughter%20was%20also%20brutally%20killed%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20violence.%20Pictured%20here%20is%20the%20skyline%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Ahmedabad%20city%20as%20the%20riots%20were%20going%20on.%20Photo%3A%20Aksi%20great%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%8