3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELosses%20all%20around%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20Sunday%2C%20August%2013%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20witnessing%20heavy%20rains.%20As%20of%20August%2017%2C%2074%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20resulting%20impacts.%20Of%20these%2C%2021%20deaths%20occurred%20in%20the%20three%20major%20landslides%20in%20Shimla%20alone%2C%20including%20at%20the%20Shiva%20temple%20in%20Summer%20Hill%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhimachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-monsoon-rain-fury-houses-collapse-fresh-landslides-imd-weather-forecast-2422806-2023-08-18%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Eight%20people%20are%20still%20feared%20trapped%20under%20debris%20here%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20days%2C%202%2C074%20people%20have%20been%20evacuated%20from%20these%20areas%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2018%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20spoke%20over%20the%20phone%20with%20his%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20counterpart%2C%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fchhattisgarh-cm-announces-rs-11-crore-aid-for-rain-ravaged-himachal-pradesh%2F632560.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20PTI.%20Baghel%20said%20that%20his%20state%20would%20contribute%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2011%20crore%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20to%20tackle%20the%20dire%20situation%20and%20help%20the%20victims%20and%20survivors.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20Baghel%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20Friday%2C%20said%20that%20a%20severe%20natural%20calamity%20hit%20the%20%E2%80%9CDevbhoomi%E2%80%9D%20(land%20of%20gods)%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20stand%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECM%20Sukhu%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20Baghel%20for%20the%20assistance%20and%20said%20that%20such%20financial%20help%20would%20make%20a%20substantial%20impact%20in%20providing%20relief%20to%20the%20disaster-hit%20families%20in%20this%20hour%20of%20calamity%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Froads-without-proper-drainage-system-will-not-be-passed-himachal-cm-sukhu-%25C2%25A0henceforth-roads-without-proper-drainage-system-will-not-be-passed-cm%25C2%25A0%2F632803.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20PTI.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20state%20has%20witnessed%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20proper%20drainage%20and%20cross-drainage%20system%20would%20be%20made%20mandatory%20for%20all%20roads%20in%20the%20state%2C%20since%20its%20lack%20caused%20water%20seepage%20and%20cracks%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20causing%20huge%20damage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98State%20calamity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20August%2018%2C%20the%20state%20government%20declared%20the%20rains%20a%20state%20calamity.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1692521158342819898%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enotification%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20(Disaster%20Management)%20said%20that%20the%20state%20has%20witnessed%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20loss%20of%20human%20lives%20and%20huge%20destruction%2C%20damage%2C%20and%20loss%20to%20public%20and%20private%20property%20during%20the%20ongoing%20monsoon%20season%E2%80%9D.%20Incessant%20rains%20led%20to%20floods%2C%20cloudbursts%2C%20landslides%2C%20and%20slope%20failure%20and%20this%20took%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20both%20lives%20and%20property%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20dwelling%20units%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed.%20There%20has%20been%20an%20unprecedented%20loss%20of%20crops%20and%20agricultural%20land.%20Thousands%20of%20tourists%20and%20local%20people%20who%20were%20stranded%20had%20to%20be%20evacuated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%20Army%2C%20NDRF%2C%20SDRE%2C%20Police%2C%20Home%20Guards%2C%20Fire%20Services%20and%20local%20volunteers.%20The%20national%20highways%2C%20state%2C%20district%20and%20local%20road%20network%20has%20been%20severely%20damaged%20and%20destroyed.%20Dozens%20of%20bridges%20have%20been%20washed%20away%20or%20damaged%20severely%20hampering%20connectivity%20and%20rescue%20efforts%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20into%20account%20this%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20grave%20situation%20leading%20%5Bto%5D%20loss%20of%20human%20life%20and%20damage%2C%20destruction%20and%20loss%20to%20public%20infrastructure%20and%20private%20property%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20declare%20the%20whole%20state%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CNatural%20Calamity%20Affected%20Area%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Government%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20providing%20all%20the%20necessary%20assistance%20for%20relief%2C%20rescue%2C%20and%20rehabilitation%20works%20throughout%20the%20state%20and%20to%20bring%20life%20of%20the%20people%20back%20to%20normalcy%20and%20mitigate%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20the%20notification%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMore%20rain%20in%20the%20coming%20days%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20rain%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20On%20Friday%2C%20August%2018%2C%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternal.imd.gov.in%2Fpress_release%2F20230818_pr_2488.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epredicted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20%E2%80%9C%20fresh%20wet%20spell%20of%20heavy%20rainfall%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20western%20Himalayan%20region%20from%20August%2020%20onward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20wanted%20that%20light%20or%20moderate%20rainfall%2C%20and%20isolated%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20are%20likely%20over%20parts%20of%20Uttarakhand%20during%20the%20next%20five%20days%2C%20over%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20August%2021%20and%2022%2C%20and%20over%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20August%2018%20and%2022.%20Uttarakhand%20may%20also%20witness%20isolated%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20on%20August%2021%20and%2022%2C%20the%20statement%20also%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692370508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11085337%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-government-declares-state-calamity-as-rains-claim-74-lives%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Damages%20to%20people%20and%20property%20due%20to%20the%20rains%20this%20season%20since%20July%20have%20resulted%20in%20losses%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%20chief%20minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-government-declares-state-calamity-as-rains-claim-74-lives%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ecuador's%20Perez%20to%20review%20mining%20contracts%20suspected%20of%20polluting%20if%20elected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692369961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102840052%2Cimgsize-41318.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fecuadors-perez-to-review