22title%22%3A%22In%20%E2%80%98Guns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%E2%80%99%2C%20Raj%20and%20DK%20Are%20in%20Good%20Form%20but%20You%20Can%20See%20the%20Gags%20Coming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F18183910%2Fimage-1234.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFilmmaker-duo%20Raj%20Nidimoru%20and%20Krishna%20DK%E2%80%99s%20(also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%E2%80%99)%20furiously%20high-priced%20stock%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20streaming%20space%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20deliver%20%5Bespecially%20since%202019%5D%20makes%20you%20wonder%20if%20they%20have%20a%20secret%20basement%20full%20of%20writers%20working%2C%20reworking%20and%20churning%20out%20gags%20on%20an%20assembly%20line.%20Such%20is%20their%20strike%20rate%20for%20landing%20them%20with%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20Bollywood%20directors%20or%20as%20the%20A-list%20showrunners%20they%E2%80%99ve%20become%20today%20%E2%80%93%20their%20work%20has%20a%20strong%20flavour%20of%20sketch-writing.%20Much%20of%20their%20writing%20outlines%20seem%20pieced%20together%20with%20one-liners%20and%20gags%2C%20while%20the%20colours%20are%20filled%20with%20deft%20action%20sequences%2C%20sincere%20romances%20and%20some%20of%20the%20most%20perceptive%2C%20adept%20acting%20on%20Indian%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20becoming%20two%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20names%20within%20the%20industry%2C%20a%20certain%20madness%20seems%20to%20run%20through%20their%20work.%20Like%20in%20their%20latest%20outing%2C%20Netflix%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20when%20a%20character%20dies%2C%20they%20mine%20the%20moment%20for%20typical%20Bollywood%20melodrama.%20The%20scene%20is%20replete%20with%20a%20man%20lying%20dead%20with%20cotton%20stuffed%20in%20his%20nostrils%2C%20a%20bawling%20mother%20seated%20next%20to%20him%20is%20beating%20her%20chest%2C%20as%20the%20violins%20screech%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20%E2%80%98hero%E2%80%99%20Tipu%20(Rajkummar%20Rao)%20looks%20on%20from%20a%20terrace%20nearby%20%E2%80%93%20riddled%20with%20guilt%20for%20being%20a%20powerless%20spectator%20of%20his%20best%20friend%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20Just%20then%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20characters%20put%20their%20arms%20around%20Tipu%2C%20consoling%20him%2C%20revealed%20to%20be%20two%20identical%20twins%20of%20the%20dead%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpgEiBaF2mHA%3Fsi%3Df05m68B-eMO_P5lD%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sadness%20is%20suddenly%20replaced%20by%20a%20chuckle.%20And%20yet%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20reached%20the%20punchline%20in%20the%20scene.%20After%20one%20of%20them%20hands%20him%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20three%20brothers%2C%20Tipu%20puts%20his%20finger%20on%20the%20friend%20while%20mourning%20him%2C%20only%20for%20the%20twin%20to%20move%20Tipu%E2%80%99s%20finger%20to%20the%20adjacent%20figure.%20From%20building%20the%20emotional%20stakes%20of%20the%20show%20and%20diffusing%20it%20with%20humour%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20in%20the%20Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%20universe%2C%20they%20can%20have%20their%20cake%20and%20eat%20it%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-created%20by%20the%20duo%20and%20Suman%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20they%E2%80%99ve%20collaborated%20with%20for%20two%20seasons%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Family%20Man%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2019)%20and%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EFarzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20in%20the%20fictitious%20town%20of%20Gulaabgunj.%20Ruled%20by%20the%20Ganchi%20family%20(Satish%20Kaushik%20plays%20the%20patriarch%2C%20Adarsh%20Gourav%20is%20the%20all-set-to-disappoint%20successor)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20town%20thrives%20on%20its%20poppy%20plantations%2C%20to%20make%20opium.%20While%20a%20section%20of%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20the%20government%20as%20a%20part%20of%20an%20agreement%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20production%20is%20grown%20for%20the%20Ganchi%20family%20and%20smuggled%20outside%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20characters%20are%20mostly%20outlines%20and%20types%2C%20with%20an%20excellent%20cast%20imbuing%20authenticity%20into%20them.%20As%20Ganchi%2C%20Kaushik%20is%20the%20foul-mouthed%20patriarch%20of%20a%20local%20empire%2C%20clinging%20on%20to%20power%20because%20he%20knows%20his%20son%20is%20no%20good.%20Gourav%20as%20Jugnu%2C%20to%20quote%20Logan%20Roy%20from%20%3Cem%3ESuccession%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%98serious%20person%E2%80%99.%20He%20hangs%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20shadow%2C%20and%20though%20isn%E2%80%99t%20disinterested%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20he%20also%20seems%20to%20know%20he%20will%20never%20measure%20up.%20Rajkummar%20Rao%2C%20plays%20a%20lovelorn%20mechanic%20%E2%80%93%20Tipu%20%E2%80%93%20son%20of%20Babu%20Tiger%2C%20one%20of%20Ganchi%E2%80%99s%20most-feared%20henchmen.%20He%20wants%20to%20escape%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sins%20by%20opening%20his%20own%20garage%2C%20but%20little%20does%20he%20know%20about%20DNA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETJ%20Bhanu%20plays%20Chandralekha%20%E2%80%93%20the%20English%20teacher%20of%20the%20local%20school%20%E2%80%93%20who%20from%20her%20muscle%20memory%20tells%20her%20students%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshut%20up%20and%20sit%20quietly%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20most%20inopportune%20situations.%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%E2%80%99s%20Arjun%20Verma%20%E2%80%93%20who%20seems%20like%20someone%20who%20has%20seen%20too%20many%20Vinod%20Khanna%2FMithun%20Chakraborty%20films%20%E2%80%93%20borrows%20his%20persona%20of%20an%20honest%20cop%20in%20a%20dishonest%20town.%20Gulshan%20Devaiah%2C%20aping%20Sanjay%20Dutt%E2%80%99s%20haircut%20from%20%3Cem%3EKhalnaayak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1993)%2C%20is%20sublime%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98imported%E2%80%99%20assassin%2C%20four-cut%20Atmaram%20%E2%80%93%20named%20after%20his%20modus%20operandi%20of%20slashing%20his%20victim%20three%20times%20before%20stabbing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20of%20the%20show%20are%20established%20in%20the%20first%20episode%20itself.%20Ganchi%20needs%20to%20deliver%20a%20lot%20of%20opium%20to%20a%20Calcutta%20cartel%2C%20fronted%20by%20a%20man%20called%20Sukanto%20(Rajatabha%20Dutta).%20If%20he%20fails%20to%20deliver%2C%20the%20cartel%20will%20send%20their%20army%20and%20annihilate%20every%20last%20one%20of%20Ganchi%E2%80%99s%20men.%20Dutta%20%E2%80%93%20who%20appeared%20in%20a%20similar%20role%20in%20Vishal%20Bhardwaj%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKaminey%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2009)%20%E2%80%93%20relishes%20his%20lines%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20way%20he%20asks%20his%20aide%20if%20the%20month%20has%2030%20or%2031%20days%2C%20after%20telling%20Ganchi%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20deliver%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%20%E2%80%9C31%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20aide%20tells%20him%2C%20to%20which%20Sukanto%20smiles%20and%20says%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEk%20extra%20din%20mil%20gaya%20aapko%2C%20lucky!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20follows%2C%20is%20a%20caper%20following%20the%20beats%20of%20Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20works%20like%20%3Cem%3E99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EShor%20In%20The%20City%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20even%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EFarzi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20multiple%20storylines%20intersect%20in%20the%20most%20unexpected%20ways%2C%20unlikely%20heroes%20emerge%20when%20one%20least%20expects%20it.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20sense%20of%20Guy%20Ritchie%E2%80%99s%20early%20work%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ELock%2C%20Stock%20%26amp%3B%20Two%20Smoking%20Barrels%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1998)%20and%20%3Cem%3ESnatch%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2000)%20here.%20Each%20character%20is%20more%20eccentric%20than%20the%20last%2C%20their%20own%20common-man%20whimsies%20morphing%20into%20humour%20in%20the%20most%20unexpected%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20enough%20of%20Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%20eccentric%20touches%20here%20%E2%80%93%20like%20a%20school%20boy%20selling%20%E2%80%98love%20letters%E2%80%99%20to%20non-English%20speakers%20by%20writing%20lyrics%20for%20English%20pop%20songs%2C%20or%20the%20awkward%20silences%20between%20an%20assassin%20and%20his%20employer%2C%20forcing%20the%20latter%20to%20scream%20%E2%80%9CHello%3F%E2%80%9D%20every%20few%20seconds.%20The%20%E2%80%9890s%20might%20seem%20like%20%E2%80%98easy%E2%80%99%20nostalgia%20%E2%80%93%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20recurring%20flavour%20with%20Netflix%20India%20%E2%80%93%20after%20the%20success%20of%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMonica!%20O%20My%20Darling%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EYeh%20Kaali%20Kaali%20Aankhen%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20honest%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%20setting%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20do%20much%20for%20the%20plot%2C%20except%20for%20arming%20it%20with%20retro%20tunes%20and%20writers%20with%20contrivance%20%E2%80%94%20given%20the%20dependence%20on%20landlines%2C%20no%20instant%20messaging%20and%20no%20navigation%20maps%2C%20etc.%20It%20does%2C%20however%2C%20have%20one%20great%20scene%20where%20Tipu%2C%20his%20friend%20and%20three%20school%20boys%20%E2%80%93%20Gangu%20(Tanishq%20Chaudhary)%2C%20Ikhlaq%20(Araham%20Sawant)%20and%20Nannu%20(Krish%20Rao)%20%E2%80%93%20listen%20to%20Bryan%20Adams%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3EEverything%20I%20Do%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20their%20eyes%20closed.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20take%20the%20plot%20forward%20in%20any%20way%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98vibe%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20decade%20is%20its%20strongest.%20Some%20of%20us%20might%20even%20get%20transported%20to%20an%20era%20of%20music%20channels%20and%20pop%20music%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20that%20viewers%20are%20catching%20up%20with%20Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20for%20orchestrated%20confusion%2C%20but%20despite%20a%20weak%20final%20stretch%2C%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20works.%20Largely%20because%20of%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20brimming%20with%20repartee%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20a%20first-rate%20ensemble%20putting%20their%20best%20foot%20forward.%20However%2C%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20well%20acquainted%20with%20the%20duo%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20you%20will%20see%20some%20of%20the%20twists%20coming.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20less%20impressive%20obviously%2C%20but%20as%20the%20epilogue%20scenes%20of%20the%20show%20suggest%20%E2%80%93%20they%E2%80%99re%20bracing%20themselves%20for%20a%20second%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20when%20the%20duo%20would%20wrap%20up%20multiple%20storylines%20and%20provide%20catharsis%20to%20its%20audience%20in%20less%20than%20two%20hours%3F%20Now%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20everything%20is%20about%20milking%20a%20premise%20till%20it%20goes%20bone-dry.%20Maybe%2C%20like%20their%20characters%2C%20the%20duo%20should%20take%20a%20moment%20and%20feel%20Bryan%20Adams%E2%80%99%20lyrics%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20I%20do%2C%20I%20do%20it%20for%20you%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20about%20their%20commitment%20towards%20cinema%2C%20their%20first%20love.%20Greatness%2C%20after%20all%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20simply%20arrive%20on%20the%20back%20of%20%E2%80%98quirk%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692367256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F18183910%2Fimage-1234.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-guns-gulaabs-raj-and-dk-are-in-good-form-but-you-can-see-the-gags-coming%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20one%20more%20caper%20film%20from%20the%20duo%20who%20made%20'Farzi'%20and%20'The%20Family%20Man'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-guns-gulaabs-raj-and-dk-are-in-good-form-but-you-can-see-the-gags-coming%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat's%20The%20Harm%3F%26quot%3B%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Giving%20Caste%20Details%20For%20Bihar%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20asked%20what%20was%20the%20harm%20if%20a%20person%20provided%20the%20details%20of%20caste%20or%20sub-caste%20during%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20when%20an%20individual's%20data%20was%20not%20going%20to%20be%20published%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%20today%20commenced%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20August%201%20decision%20of%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court%20which%20gave%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20the%20caste%20survey.%20Some%20of%20these%20petitions%20have%20claimed%20the%20exercise%20was%20an%20infringement%20of%20people's%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20gives%20the%20name%20of%20his%20caste%20or%20sub-caste%2C%20and%20if%20that%20data%20is%20not%20published%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20harm.%20What%20is%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20released%20is%20cumulative%20figures.%20How%20does%20that%20affect%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%3F%20What%20questions%20(in%20the%20questionnaire%20prepared%20for%20the%20survey)%20do%20you%20think%20are%20contrary%20to%20Article%2021%20(right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20asked%20senior%20advocate%20CS%20Vaidyanathan%2C%20appearing%20for%20NGO%20'Youth%20for%20Equality'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20is%20among%20various%20petitioners%20that%20have%20challenged%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20decision%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Shyam%20Divan%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20said%20the%20caste%20survey%20was%20completed%20on%20August%206%20and%20the%20data%20gathered%20uploaded%20by%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Divan%20it%20is%20not%20issuing%20notice%20on%20the%20petitions%20as%20then%20the%20question%20will%20arise%20about%20interim%20relief%20and%20the%20hearing%20will%20get%20pushed%20back%20to%20November%20or%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Aprajita%20Singh%2C%20representing%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20they%20are%20aware%20that%20the%20exercise%20has%20been%20completed%20but%20would%20argue%20for%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20stay%20something%20unless%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20is%20made%20out%20as%20there%20is%20a%20judgement%20of%20the%20high%20court%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20state%20government.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20the%20data%20has%20been%20uploaded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20the%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%2C%20which%20has%20been%20collected%20during%20the%20survey%2C%20has%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20BIJAGA%20(Bihar%20Jaati%20Adharit%20Ganana)%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Divan%20there%20are%20two%20things-%20one%20that%20individual%20data%20will%20not%20be%20made%20public%20and%20two%20that%20the%20cumulative%20data%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20different%20departments%20for%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Divan%20said%20that's%20the%20point%20if%20individual%20data%20is%20not%20to%20be%20released%2C%20then%20where%20is%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%20unfortunately%20in%20Bihar%2C%20normally%20the%20caste%20of%20an%20individual%20is%20known%20to%20neighbours%20although%20such%20a%20situation%20does%20not%20exist%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVadiyanathan%20contended%20a%20constitution%20bench%20of%20this%20court%20had%20in%202017%20ruled%20that%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20cannot%20be%20infringed%20upon%20except%20under%20a%20fair%2C%20just%20and%20reasonable%20law%20with%20a%20legitimate%20aim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20law%20but%20an%20executive%20order%20(for%20caste%20survey)%20and%20no%20reasons%20have%20been%20given%20and%20communicated%20in%20that%20order....What%20is%20infringed%20is%20Article%2014%20and%2021%20(right%20to%20equality%20before%20law%20and%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty)%20and%20a%20normal%20executive%20order%20will%20not%20suffice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20notification%20for%20caste%20survey%20is%20not%20a%20quasi-judicial%20order%20where%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20communicate%20the%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20administrative%20decision%2C%20where%20there%20may%20not%20be%20much%20detail%20for%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaidyanathan%20said%20mere%20notification%20cannot%20take%20the%20nature%20of%20statute%20or%20law%20as%20envisioned%20in%20the%202017%20verdict%20in%20the%20KS%20Puttaswamy%20case%2C%20which%20dealt%20with%20the%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Article%2021%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20invaded%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20supported%20by%20a%20statute%20not%20a%20notification.%20Please%20see%20the%20questions%20which%20were%20asked%20from%20the%20public%20in%20the%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaidyanathan%20told%20the%20bench%2C%20while%20referring%20to%20the%20questionnaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20asked%20him%20which%20questions%20he%20thought%20were%20contrary%20to%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20infringed%20the%20right%20to%20privacy.%20Vaidyanathan%20responded%20by%20saying%20people%20have%20been%20asked%20about%20their%20gender%2C%20caste%2C%20income%20and%20answering%20all%20these%20questions%20have%20been%20made%20mandatory.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20related%20to%20caste%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20privacy.%20All%20the%2017%20questions%20are%20made%20mandatory%20to%20be%20answered%20by%20the%20public%20and%20only%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20is%20voluntary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20real%20question%20is%20can%20the%20public%20be%20asked%20to%20furnish%20these%20details%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20there%20was%20no%20penalty%20if%20the%20public%20does%20not%20give%20these%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20adjourned%20the%20hearing%20for%20August%2021%20after%20senior%20advocate%20Aprajita%20Singh%20said%20she%20needs%20time%20to%20make%20her%20submissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%207%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court's%20order%20giving%20the%20go-ahead%20for%20the%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20pleas%20filed%20by%20NGOs%20'Youth%20for%20Equality'%20and%20'Ek%20Soch%20Ek%20Paryas'%2C%20another%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20Nalanda%20resident%20Akhilesh%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20contended%20that%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20state%20government%20for%20the%20exercise%20is%20against%20the%20constitutional%20mandate.%20There%20are%20some%20other%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar's%20petition%20says%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20constitutional%20mandate%2C%20only%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20empowered%20to%20conduct%20a%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%2C%20filed%20through%20advocate%20Barun%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20said%20the%20entire%20exercise%20of%20conducting%20a%20%26quot%3Bcensus%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%20without%20authority%20and%20legislative%20competence%2C%20and%20reeks%20of%20malafide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20said%20in%20its%20101-page%20verdict%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20find%20the%20action%20of%20the%20state%20to%20be%20perfectly%20valid%2C%20initiated%20with%20due%20competence%20with%20the%20legitimate%20aim%20of%20providing%20development%20with%20justice....%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headlin