miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327625%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20govt%20school%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20launching%20the%20non-profit%2C%20Abhishek%20started%20his%20journey%20with%20a%20government%20school%20for%20girls.%20Talking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20in%202017%2C%20there%20were%20only%2079%20girls%20enrolled%20in%20the%20school.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20with%20the%20school%20to%20transform%20the%20education%20system%20with%20digital%20learning%20methods%2C%20the%20enrollment%20of%20girls%20increased%20to%20129.%20This%20impact%20encouraged%20us%20to%20understand%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20meaningful%20for%20the%20chil