this%20means%20sacking%20%E2%80%93%20educator%20Karan%20Sangwan%20for%20the%20action%20of%20telling%20his%20students%20to%20vote%20for%20educated%20leaders%20and%20its%20subsequent%20explanation%20as%20to%20why%20it%20did%20so%2C%20Unacademy%2C%20an%20education%20platform%2C%20is%20both%20right%20and%20wrong.%20But%2C%20from%20purely%20a%20commercial%20perspective%2C%20the%20company%20has%20possibly%20scored%20a%20huge%20self-goal%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20could%20cost%20it%20future%20enrolments%20as%20well%20as%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%2C%20because%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwrongly%20influence%E2%80%9D%20students%20by%20urging%20them%20to%20use%20the%20power%20of%20vote%20effectively%20by%20voting%20for%20the%20best%20candidate%20%E2%80%93%20read%20literate%20%E2%80%93%20in%20an%20election%20is%20not%20the%20job%20of%20a%20teacher.%20Unacademy%20can%20always%20buttress%20its%20assertion%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20even%20our%20Constitution%20drafters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20mandatory%20for%20a%20candidate%20to%20hold%20a%20college%20of%20university%20degree%20in%20order%20to%20contest%20an%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudies%20have%20shown%20that%20educated%20leaders%20are%20not%20always%20better.%20Look%20around%20you%20these%20days%20and%20you%20will%20also%20realise%20that%20being%20educated%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20make%20one%20wiser%20or%20smarter.%20Most%20of%20us%2C%20especially%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20members%2C%20are%20getting%20re-educated%20by%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20universities%20%E2%80%93%20WhatsApp%20and%20other%20social%20media.%20But%20being%20educated%20also%20gives%20us%20an%20ability%20to%20find%20answers%20to%20several%20of%20society%E2%80%99s%20problems.%20That%2C%20possibly%2C%20was%20what%20Sangwan%20was%20thinking%20when%20he%20suggested%20that%20his%20students%20elect%20educated%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20making%20it%20mandatory%20for%20candidates%20for%20MP%20and%20MLA%20elections%20to%20possess%20some%20basic%20minimum%20education%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20which%20might%20be%20left%20to%20the%20legislatures.%20If%20the%20legislature%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20prescribing%20qualification%20feels%20that%20literacy%20qualification%20is%20a%20necessary%20one%2C%20I%20no%20doubt%20think%20that%20they%20will%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20while%20Ambedkar%20took%20a%20nuanced%20view%2C%20something%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20also%20agreed%20with%2C%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20first%20President%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20served%20as%20president%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20was%20among%20those%20who%20had%20hoped%20that%20education%20would%20be%20a%20key%20criteria%20for%20future%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20only%20two%20regrets%20which%20I%20must%20share%20with%20the%20honourable%20members.%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20have%20some%20qualifications%20laid%20down%20for%20members%20of%20the%20legislatures.%20It%20is%20anomalous%20that%20we%20should%20insist%20upon%20high%20qualifications%20for%20those%20who%20administer%20or%20help%20in%20administering%20the%20law%20but%20none%20for%20those%20who%20make%20it%20except%20that%20they%20are%20elected.%20A%20law%20giver%20requires%20intellectual%20equipment%20but%20even%20more%20than%20that%20capacity%20to%20take%20a%20balanced%20view%20of%20things%2C%20to%20act%20independently%20and%20above%20all%20to%20be%20true%20to%20those%20fundamental%20things%20of%20life%20%E2%80%93%20in%20one%20word%20%E2%80%93%20to%20have%20character%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Unacademy%2C%20once%20it%20is%20done%20with%20parting%20ways%20with%20all%20educated%2C%20opinionated%20educators%20on%20its%20payroll%2C%20the%20company%20can%20do%20all%20of%20us%20a%20favour%20by%20making%20public%20its%20%E2%80%9CCode%20of%20Conduct%E2%80%9D%20on%20what%20its%20staff%20can%20tell%20or%20teach%20the%20students%20and%20what%20not.%20That%20will%20also%20further%20help%20the%20unicorn%20which%20is%20reeling%20under%20losses%20%E2%80%93%20in%20fiscal%202021-22%2C%20despite%20higher%20revenues%2C%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finc42.com%2Fbuzz%2Funacademys-fy22-losses-shoot-up-to-inr-2693-cr-despite-80-higher-revenue%2F%5C%22%3Elosses%20went%20up%20to%20Rs%202%2C848%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20company%20has%20seen%20some%20of%20the%20highest%20layoffs%20in%20the%20sector%20%E2%80%93%20rein%20in%20its%20balance-sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20one%20must%20say%20that%20Unacademy%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20more%20wrong.%20Because%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F181312133%2F%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20did%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20that%20too%20in%20a%20case%20dealing%20with%20mandatory%20educational%20qualifications%2C%20among%20other%20criteria%2C%20for%20panchayati%20raj%20representatives%20in%20Haryana%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20only%20education%20which%20gives%20a%20human%20being%20the%20power%20to%20discriminate%20between%20right%20and%20wrong%2C%20good%20and%20bad.%20Therefore%2C%20prescription%20of%20an%20educational%20qualification%20is%20not%20irrelevant%20for%20better%20administration%20of%20the%20panchayats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20trying%20to%20be%20on%20the%20safe%20side%20of%20those%20who%20used%20social%20media%20to%20attack%20it%20after%20Sangwan%E2%80%99s%20video%2C%20Unacademy%E2%80%99s%20focus%20should%20be%20to%20shore%20up%20its%20flailing%20balance%20sheet%20and%20attract%20more%20talented%20educators%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20instead%20of%20firing%20people%20like%20Sangwan%2C%20it%20must%20try%20and%20attract%20more%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElse%2C%20the%20question%20on%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20mind%2C%20especially%20its%20prospective%20hires%2C%20would%20be%3A%20What%20will%20the%20company%20do%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20backlash%20against%20something%20that%20it%20or%20one%20of%20its%20employees%20does%20in%20the%20future%3F%20How%20many%20Sangwans%20will%20it%20fire%20to%20appease%20the%20trolls%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20purpose%20of%20education%2C%20it%20must%20realise%2C%20is%20to%20be%20enlightened%2C%20alive%20to%20what%20is%20going%20on%20around%20us%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20able%20to%20take%20a%20morally%20correct%20stand.%20Unacademy%20is%20a%20business%20and%20while%20in%20India%20you%20need%20to%20be%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20government%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20even%20your%20lawful%20business%2C%20there%20must%20have%20been%20a%20better%20way%20to%20sidestep%20the%20mudslinging%20that%20followed%20Sangwan%E2%80%99s%20video%20without%20knowingly%20stepping%20into%20the%20mud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%2C%20however%2C%20has%20happened%20is%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20backlash%20that%20has%20come%20Unacademy%E2%80%99s%20way%20after%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funacademy%2Fstatus%2F1692221440568009124%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20had%20parted%20ways%20with%20Sangwan%20has%20turned%20the%20entire%20incident%20into%20a%20massive%20negative%20PR%20exercise%20for%20the%20struggling%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20negative%20PR%20is%20such%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20sponsorship%20of%20cricket%20tournaments%20or%20series%20will%20earn%20it%20brownie%20points%20or%20erase%20the%20last%20few%20days%20from%20public%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20from%20now%2C%20unless%20it%20manages%20to%20do%20something%20positive%20on%20a%20very%20large%20scale%2C%20the%20first%20things%20that%20will%20hit%20our%20Google%20feed%20when%20you%20type%20Unacademy%20could%20possibly%20be%20news%20stories%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20them%20negative%20%E2%80%93%20about%20its%20recent%20travails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20only%20people%20to%20blame%20are%20the%20top%20executives%20of%20the%20unicorn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Unacademy%20isn%E2%80%99t%20alone%20in%20staring%20at%20this%20self-made%20PR%20disaster.%20Recently%2C%20Ashoka%20University%2C%20another%20educational%20institute%20%E2%80%93%20this%20one%20running%20out%20of%20a%20brick%20and%20mortar%20structure%20in%20Sonepat%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20be%20the%20citadel%20of%20liberal%20arts%20and%20social%20sciences%20education%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20too%20inflicted%20upon%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fecon-dept-says-ashoka-governing-body-interference-forcing-scholars-to-operate-in-environment-of-fear%5C%22%3Ean%20agonising%20self-goal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20possibly%20facilitating%20the%20sudden%20resignation%20of%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%2C%20following%20a%20controversy%20over%20his%20research%20paper%20that%20suggested%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%20a%20disproportionate%20share%20of%20closely%20contested%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20especially%20in%20states%20where%20it%20was%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Ashoka%20poked%20another%20hole%20into%20its%20position%20as%20a%20fledgling%20centre%20of%20excellence%20for%20liberal%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20time%20that%20it%20has%20been%20functioning%2C%20Ashoka%20University%20has%20seen%20several%20high-profile%20and%20controversial%20exits%20that%20could%20reduce%20the%20aura%20that%20attracts%20students%20to%20its%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Unacademy%2C%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20founders%20too%20need%20to%20calculate%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20bad%20PR%20and%20do%20some%20urgent%20damage%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EManeesh%20Chhibber%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%