spacecraft-s-lander-123081800457_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fisro-releases-visuals-of-moon-captured-by-chandrayaan-3-spacecraft-s-lander-123081800457_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Naxalbari%2C%20A%20Battle%20Again%20for%20Land%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F18145327%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-30-at-6.12.03-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaxalbari%20(Bengal)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Naxalbari%20area%2C%20once%20known%20for%20fiery%20political%20struggle%20that%20attracted%20the%20best%20minds%20of%20Bengal%2C%20is%20now%20playing%20host%20to%20a%20quieter%20but%20no%20less%20significant%20struggle%20over%20land%20ownership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20picturesque%20terrain%20of%20the%20Duars%20in%20West%20Bengal%20has%20a%20history%20etched%20in%20both%20rebellion%20and%20controversy.%20Since%20the%201970s%2C%20the%20very%20mention%20of%20Naxalbari%20has%20been%20synonymous%20with%20resistance%2C%20inspiring%20generations%20of%20young%20women%20and%20men%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo.%20Here%2C%20among%20the%20verdant%20hills%20and%20rustic%20landscapes%2C%20the%20seeds%20of%20a%20left-wing%20revolutionary%20movement%20were%20sown.%20This%20movement%20aimed%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20land%20reform%20and%20social%20equality%20and%20ensure%20the%20rights%20of%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FCharu_majumdar.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charu%20Mazumdar.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22262%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-157438%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECharu%20Mazumdar.%20Photo%3A%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20shadow%20of%20towering%20leaders%20like%20Charu%20Majumdar%2C%20Kanu%20Sanyal%2C%20Jangal%20Santal%2C%20Mahadev%20Mukherjee%20and%20Saroj%20Dutt%2C%20Naxalbari%20became%20the%20epicentre%20of%20an%20ideological%20battle%20that%20reshaped%20the%20contours%20of%20Indian%20society.%20The%20formal%20break%20of%20these%20leaders%20with%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20in%201969%20meant%20that%20the%20Communist%20party%20split%20twice%20in%20the%201960s.%20The%20expectation%20of%20young%20minds%20confident%20of%20a%20revolution%20collided%20with%20the%20entrenched%20interests%20of%20landlords%2C%20who%20held%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebenami%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20landholdings%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20wave%20of%20resistance%20that%20swept%20the%20state%20and%20whose%20ripples%20were%20felt%20all%20over%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThousands%20of%20young%20lives%20were%20lost%2C%20families%20were%20torn%20apart%20and%20an%20entire%20generation%20grappled%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20pursuit%20of%20change.%20Decades%20later%2C%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20righteousness%20of%20the%20Naxalite%20movement%2C%20as%20it%20came%20to%20be%20called%2C%20continues%20to%20reverberate%2C%20with%20differing%20perspectives%20echoing%20through%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20conscience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20Naxalbari%20uprising%20in%201967%20was%20the%20issue%20of%20land%20reform%20and%20agrarian%20rights.%20The%20movement%20aimed%20to%20redistribute%20land%20to%20the%20landless%20and%20poor%20farmers.%20The%20then-Left%20Front%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20launch%20Operation%20Barga%2C%20a%20programme%20to%20grant%20land%20rights%20to%20sharecroppers%20in%201978%20was%20also%20one%20that%20was%20responding%20to%20demands%20and%20agitations%20raised%20by%20such%20movements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaxalbari%20led%20to%20a%20notable%20shift%20in%20political%20and%20social%20dynamics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20year%20now%20is%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20generational%20sharecroppers%20who%20were%20once%20granted%20land%20rights%20in%20Naxalbari%20decades%20ago%2C%20complain%20that%20their%20names%20now%20no%20longer%20feature%20on%20the%20official%20records.%20Right%20to%20Information%20activists%20and%20local%20leaders%20say%20that%20while%20this%20vested%20land%20had%20been%20under%20their%20name%20so%20far%2C%20government%20records%20are%20now%20being%20surreptitiously%20changed%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20this%20land%20to%20be%20sold.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20happening%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20those%20who%20are%20living%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20from%20the%201970s%2C%20sharecroppers%20in%20the%20area%20had%20been%20given%20land%20parcels.%20Although%20this%20land%20technically%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20the%20sharecroppers%2C%20they%20are%20registered%20as%20its%20users%20on%20government%20records.%20This%20offers%20them%20safety%20of%20ownership%20and%20ensures%20future%20generations%20also%20get%20to%20use%20the%20land.%20However%2C%20now%20these%20records%20are%20being%20tampered%20with%20or%20invalidated%2C%20many%20in%20the%20area%20complain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20say%20that%20their%20land%20is%20now%20entered%20under%20other%20names%20who%20end%20up%20selling%20them%20at%20significantly%20inflated%20prices.%20There%20is%20a%20veritable%20land%20mafia%20operating%20in%20the%20area%2C%20say%20activists.%20These%20alleged%20mafia%20are%20looking%20to%20make%20large-scale%20constructions%20of%20gated%20communities%20and%20holiday%20homes%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d28519.36463495894!2d88.18302953410137!3d26.68302241419713!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e44c7a77405217%253A0x1482b15a1eca252a!2sNaxalbari%252C%2520West%2520Bengal%2520734429!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1692351380086!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECuriously%2C%20local%20real%20estate%20managers%20have%20also%20noted%20a%20surge%20in%20real%20estate%20investments%20from%20residents%20of%20northeastern%20states%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20Real%20estate%20agent%20Ajit%2C%20who%20works%20at%20Naxalbari%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBig%20industrialists%20and%20real%20estate%20tycoons%20from%20Kolkata%20started%20buying%20vast%20stretches%20of%20land%20here%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%20Many%20well-known%20political%20leaders%20also%20made%20purchases%20after%202011%20%5Bafter%20there%20was%20a%20change%20of%20government%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20took%20charge%5D.%20Since%20then%2C%20Bagdogra%2C%20the%20airport%20which%20is%2010%20km%20from%20Siliguri%2C%20has%20undergone%20significant%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20numerous%20people%20from%20the%20northeastern%20states%20and%20from%20Nepal%20have%20been%20sending%20advance%20payments%20to%20buy%20land%20or%20ready-to-move-in%20flats%20in%20the%20area%2C%20Ajit%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20in%20the%20northeast%20states%20view%20Bengal%20as%20a%20relatively%20safe%20area%20amidst%20the%20prevailing%20political%20unrest%20in%20the%20region.%20This%20correspondent%20spoke%20to%20a%20businessman%20from%20Manipur%20before%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20state%20in%20early%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSiliguri%20will%20become%20a%20corridor%20since%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20invested%20heavily%20in%20the%20chicken%20neck%20areas.%20Here%2C%20we%20have%20convenient%20access%20to%20private%20school%20education%20and%20healthcare%20services%2C%20and%20the%20airport%20is%20well-connected%20by%20road.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20numerous%20families%20are%20now%20opting%20to%20move%20near%20Siliguri%20to%20enjoy%20comparative%20peace%20and%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20surging%20demand%20for%20land%20has%20led%20to%20the%20depletion%20of%20common%20land%20stock%2C%20and%20property%20registered%20in%20the%20names%20of%20tribal%20residents%2C%20sharecroppers%2C%20or%20recorded%20as%20vested%20and%20plantation%20land%20are%20now%20being%20labelled%20as%20%E2%80%98vastu%E2%80%99land%20and%20sold%20for%20residential%20purposes.%20Many%20landowners%20are%20completely%20unaware%20of%20these%20transfers.%20Locals%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20police%20support%20to%20such%20transfer%20of%20land%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F20154128%2FNaxalbari-police-repression-cpiml.org_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F20154128%2FNaxalbari-police-repression-cpiml.org_.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F20154128%2FNaxalbari-police-repression-cpiml.org_-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F20154128%2FNaxalbari-police-repression-cpiml.org_-1024x672.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-281352%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22787%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20repression%20at%20Naxalbari.%20Photo%3A%20cpiml.org%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELathru%20Santal%20from%20the%20Hatighisha%20area%20was%20once%20involved%20in%20the%20Naxal%20movement.%20In%201978%2C%20the%20government%20accorded%20him%207%20bighas%20of%20land.%20Although%20Lathru%20is%20no%20longer%20alive%2C%20his%20progeny%20remain%2C%20and%20the%20land%E2%80%99s%20value%20has%20now%20reached%20Rs%2070%20lakh.%20However%2C%20the%20title%20of%20the%20land%20has%20recently%20been%20changed.%20And%20Lathru%E2%80%99s%20family%20discovered%20that%20it%20had%20been%20sold%20under%20a%20new%20plot%20number.%20According%20to%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%E2%80%99s%20land%20record%2C%20the%20mentioned%20lands%20in%20South%20Bagdogra%20are%20classified%20as%20government%20vested%20lands%20under%20JL%20No.%2099%2C%20Plot%20No.%20295%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20JL%20No.%2094%2C%20Mauza%20Dubirvedi%2C%20Plot%20No.%20603%2C%20Khatian%20No.%20443%2C%20Deed%20No.%20752%2F2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20teacher%20in%20Naxalbari%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20said%20that%20bureaucracy%2C%20right%20from%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20Bengal%2C%20is%20to%20blame.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20they%20are%20openly%20looting%20the%20land.%20I%20have%20lived%20in%20this%20area%20for%2054%20years%2C%20and%20I%20fear%20that%20the%20mafia%20may%20resort%20to%20violence%20with%20help%20from%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20say%20that%20around%2050%20agriculturist%20families%20from%20the%20north%20Bengal%20region%20have%20discovered%20that%20their%20land%20has%20been%20sold%20without%20their%20consent.%20A%20movement%20against%20eventual%20eviction%20began%20under%20Haripad%20Singh%20of%20Bara%20Maniram%20village%20in%20Naxalbari%20and%20Veena%20Singh%20of%20Kamli%20Munda%20Kedugapur%20in%20Hatighisha.%20The%20two%20leaders%20tell%20this%20correspondent%20that%20they%20have%20cause%20for%20worry%20because%20due%20to%20changes%20in%20the%20Mechi%20river%E2%80%99s%20course%2C%20land%20along%20the%20riverbanks%2C%20previously%20lost%20to%20floods%2C%20has%20become%20more%20fertile%20for%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20office%20of%20Biplab%20Haldar%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20overseeing%20the%20land%20records%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20online%20land%20portal%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbanglarbhumi.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ebanglarbhumi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20responded%20to%20the%20mounting%20complaints.%20The%20office%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20entire%20land%20map%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20digitised%20and%20accessible%20online.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20admitted%20to%20hearing%20about%20discrepancies%20in%20land%20ownership%2C%20where%20names%2C%20land%20markers%2C%20and%20Khatian%20numbers%20have%20been%20changed%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20rightful%20landowners.%20However%2C%20they%20asserted%20that%20such%20actions%20would%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20district%20land%20office%2C%20not%20at%20the%20block%20land%20offices.%20Access%20to%20the%20necessary%20passwords%20lies%20solely%20with%20the%20district%20land%20office%2C%20preventing%20the%20block%20land%20offices%20from%20making%20such%20alterations%2C%20the%20office%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnaxalbari-communism-maoism%5C%22%3EFifty%20Years%20After%20Naxalbari%2C%20Popular%20Movements%20Still%20Have%20Lessons%20to%20Learn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20as%20yet%20unclear%20if%20the%20government%20has%20launched%20enquiries%20into%20the%20illegal%20transfers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDarjeeling%20district%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Siliguri%20mayor%20Gautam%20Dev%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20heard%20of%20such%20incidents%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20occupy%20government%20land.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20area%20have%20been%20urged%20to%20protect%20the%20land%20and%20treat%20it%20as%20their%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGautam%20Ghosh%2C%20leader%20of%20Chia%20Kaman%20Mazdoor%20Union%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20tea%20workers%20in%20Darjeeling%20district%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20we%20are%20discovering%20alarming%20instances%20of%20the%20use%20of%20fake%20documents.%20Land%20rights%20for%20the%20landless%20and%20sharecroppers%20were%20implemented%20during%20the%20Left%20era%2C%20which%20provided%20them%20with%20legal%20papers.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20now%20witnessing%20that%20those%20who%20have%20been%20granted%20land%20plots%20have%20suddenly%20become%20encroachers.%20This%20requires%20a%20high-level%20impartial%20inquiry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Phansidewa%20Mauza%20JL%20No.%2087%2C%20where%20vested%20land%20ownership%20has%20been%20manipulated%2C%20and%20thus%20all%20the%20plot%20numbers%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20278%2F279%2F280.%20The%20current%20market%20value%20of%20this%20land%20is%20over%20Rs%2030%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAshok%20Bhattacharya%2C%20a%20senior%20CPI(M)%20leader%20from%20Siliguri%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20involved%20in%20looting%20land%20through%20the%20land%20mafia%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20a%20party%20to%20it.%20Many%20government%20officials%20must%20be%20involved%20for%20the%20recorded%20land%20ownership%20numbers%20to%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20from%20Naxalbari%20reveals%20families%20fighting%20desperately%20to%20protect%20their%20land%2C%20expressing%20emotions%20akin%20to%20losing%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%