ists%20during%20the%20press%20briefing%20after%20the%20Bali%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20helps%20resolve%20the%20border%20crisis%2C%20there%20could%20be%20nothing%20better%20for%20India%20and%20the%20region.%20The%20operative%20word%20here%20is%20%E2%80%9Cresolve%E2%80%9D%2C%20because%20this%20is%20the%20most%20worrying%20part%20of%20the%20latest%20joint%20statement.%20Consider%20this%20bit%3A%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussion%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Western%20sector%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIpso%20facto%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethis%20implies%20that%20many%20issues%20have%20been%20resolved%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20a%20phrasing%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fe611e5bd-5c26-47a2-80ca-651ad2c671e0%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fe611e5bd-5c26-47a2-80ca-651ad2c671e0%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw05lQOHLx8lHtc4ShrxnIWc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20recently%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20as%20well.%20These%20areas%20of%20Chinese%20ingress%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Cfriction%20points%E2%80%9D%20as%20Jaishankar%20calls%20them%2C%20which%20stand%20resolved%20as%20per%20this%20description%20are%3A%20Galwan%2C%20Gogra%2C%20Kugrang%20valley%20(widely%20misreported%20as%20Hot%20Springs)%2C%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20Pangong%20lake%20and%20the%20Kailash%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20at%20these%20places%20is%20only%20disengagement%2C%20which%20means%20that%20soldiers%20from%20both%20armies%20who%20were%20deployed%20in%20an%20eyeball-to-eyeball%20confrontation%20have%20stepped%20back%20by%20a%20few%20kilometres.%20Separating%20them%20is%20a%20buffer%20zone%20or%20a%20not-patrol%20area%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20mostly%20in%20the%20areas%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20patrolling%20till%20May%202020.%20This%20is%20nothing%20close%20to%20resolution%2C%20which%20means%20a%20return%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%20bellum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20situation%20as%20it%20existed%20before%20the%20crisis%20began%20in%202020.%20That%20would%20mean%20de-escalation%2C%20where%20additional%20forces%20step%20back%20to%20their%20semi-permanent%20bases%20100-150%20km%20away%2C%20and%20finally%20de-induction%2C%20where%20additional%20troops%20that%20came%20into%20the%20Ladakh%20sector%20are%20sent%20back%20to%20their%20peacetime%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20have%20publicly%20refused%20to%20accept%20any%20return%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%20bellum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20worthwhile%20conversation%20in%20these%2019%20rounds%20about%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%20from%20Ladakh.%20Indian%20forces%20continue%20to%20be%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fa8bfec63-5a7e-4b87-93cf-b3d2d6924bc9%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fa8bfec63-5a7e-4b87-93cf-b3d2d6924bc9%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1N3xESq-6PjtrYo0H-yy1_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenied%20access%20to%2026%20of%20the%2065%20patrolling%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(many%20of%20them%20well%20inside%20the%20LAC%20on%20the%20Indian%20side)%2C%20including%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20disengagement%20has%20taken%20place.%20Disengagement%20is%20a%20welcome%20exercise%20as%20a%20military%20expedient%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20escalation%20by%20separating%20the%20soldiers%20of%20two%20armies%2C%20but%20it%20is%20nowhere%20near%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Chinese%20would%20want%20to%20depict%20disengagement%20as%20resolution%20is%20understandable%20because%20it%20is%20to%20their%20advantage%2C%20but%20why%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20agreeing%20to%20such%20a%20proposition%20is%20hard%20to%20grasp.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20has%20witnessed%20this%20play%20in%20Doklam%20in%202017.%20After%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20met%20in%20Germany%20during%20the%20Doklam%20crisis%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20announced%20disengagement%20%E2%80%93%20again%20portrayed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20that%20allowed%20Modi%20to%20travel%20to%20China%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F8f9d83d3-7b5d-425e-9f1c-38176fad01e5%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F8f9d83d3-7b5d-425e-9f1c-38176fad01e5%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw050sc3Z58eMVU7wyHFh79T%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacknowledge%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20Chinese%20had%20stepped%20back%20by%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20and%20constructed%20massive%20military%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20area.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Indian%20soldiers%20had%20returned%20to%20their%20original%20deployment%20positions%20under%20the%20disengagement%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20wants%20to%20see%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20Doklam%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%2